and%2011%20a.m.%20was%20%26quot%3Bprime%20time%26quot%3B%20for%20robbery%2C%20Gomez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGomez%20said%20she%20also%20looked%20out%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-home-security-system%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurity%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Rather%20than%20deter%20her%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20one%20let%20her%20know%20there%20was%20something%20valuable%20and%20worth%20stealing%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20in%20Florida%2C%20where%20she's%20from%2C%20the%20police%20would%20call%20the%20house%20if%20the%20alarm%20went%20off%20and%20if%20nobody%20answered%2C%20they%20would%20send%20officers%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20wasted%20a%20lot%20of%20police%20time%2C%20so%20they%20changed%20the%20rules.%20Since%20around%202006%2C%20Gomez%20explained%2C%20unless%20the%20police%20or%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fnest-secure-alarm-system-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealarm%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20company%20makes%20contact%20with%20the%20homeowner%2C%20officers%20won't%20attend%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20knew%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Gomez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20would%20wait%20for%20the%20alarm%20to%20go%20off%2C%20then%20she%20knew%20if%20the%20homeowner%20was%20contacted%2C%20she%20had%20about%2010%20to%2015%20minutes%20before%20the%20cops%20showed%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20for%20me%20was%20all%20I%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20now%20what%20I%20needed%20to%20ensure%20was%20that%20there%20was%20a%20window%20somewhere%20low%20enough%20where%20I%20could%20use%20tools%20that%20I%20had.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGomez%20had%20glass-cutting%20tools%2C%20including%20gloves%2C%20a%20hammer%2C%20and%20a%20sucker%20to%20pull%20the%20sliced%20glass%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20thing%20she%20looked%20out%20for%20was%20a%20sign%20for%20