20he%20first%20tried%20ayahuasca%20about%20a%20decade%20ago%20at%20a%20yoga%20studio%20in%20Brooklyn.%20He'd%20found%20success%20earlier%20in%20his%20career%20building%20and%20then%20exiting%20two%20tech%20startups.%20With%20those%20successes%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20a%20%2415%20million%20funding%20round%20%E2%80%94%20his%20investors%20then%20asked%20Evans%20to%20raise%20another%20%2420%20million.%20But%20he%20wasn't%20feeling%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20moment%2C%20like%20something%20in%20me%20just%20like%20kind%20of%20sunk%2C%26quot%3B%20Evans%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20to%20keep%20doing%20this.%26quot%3B%20He%20wasn't%20feeling%20connected%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bunhealthy%2C%20unneeded%26quot%3B%20products%20the%20company%20was%20selling%20to%20large%20corporations.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20investors%20grew%20tired%20of%20his%20reluctance%20to%20raise%20funds%20and%20fired%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvans%20said%20that%20caused%20everything%20to%20shift.%20He%20was%20married%20and%20living%20in%20New%20York%20City%20but%20was%20unhappy.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20done%20basically%20all%20the%20things%20%E2%80%94%20checked%20all%20the%20boxes%20%E2%80%94%20that%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20do%20to%20live%20a%20happy%2C%20fulfilled%20life%20and%20I%20wasn't%20feeling%20any%20of%20it.%20I%20felt%20very%20disconnected%20from%20myself%20and%20from%20a%20lot%20of%20areas%20of%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20around%20the%20time%20he%20first%20tried%20ayahuasca.%20Evans%20said%20the%20experience%20let%20him%20get%20a%20clearer%20picture%20of%20what%20would%20bring%20him%20joy%20and%20fulfillment.%20So%20he%20left%20New%20York%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20marriage%20%E2%80%94%20and%20began%20to%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Evans%20is%20based%20full%20time%20in%20Costa%20Rica.%20And%20he%20sees%20his%20work%20at%201heart%20as%20part%20of%20his%20purpose.%20The%20program%20involves%20more%20than%20just%20ayahuasca%20ceremonies%2C%20though%20they're%20a%20major%20component.%20There's%20also%20yoga%2C%20breath%20work%2C%20and%20meditation.%20The%20price%20of%20the%20eight-week%20endeavor%2C%20excluding%20airfare%20to%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20ranges%20from%20%245%2C000%20to%20%249%2C000%2C%20Evans%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BYou%20essentially%20lose%20control%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVaisberg's%20experience%20wasn't%20just%20about%20the%20ayahuasca%2C%20which%20he%20hadn't%20tried%20before%20his%201heart%20trip.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20have%20been%20100%25%20worth%20it%20if%20we%20never%20touched%20ayahuasca%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVaisberg%20added%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth-news%2Fayahuasca-psychoactive-drink-can-ease-mental-health-issues-but-there-are-side-effects%23New-study-on-Ayahuasca%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eencounter%20with%20ayahuasca%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20often%20made%20from%20a%20pair%20of%20plants%20that%20grow%20in%20the%20Amazon%2C%20wasn't%20easy.%20%26quot%3BYou%20essentially%20completely%20lose%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20is%20coming%20up%20and%20showing%20you%2C%20you're%20living%20through%20it%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20ceremony%20was%20%26quot%3Breally%20dark%2C%26quot%3B%20Vaisberg%20said.%20So%20was%20the%20first%20part%20of%20the%20second%20ceremony.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20had%20lost%20my%20mind%20and%20then%20I%20had%20to%20go%20through%20the%20depths%20of%20my%20own%20insanity%20to%2C%20like%2C%20come%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20But%20then%20it%20flipped.%20%26quot%3BStarting%20with%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%20second%20ceremony%2C%20it%20was%20the%20most%20beautiful%2096%20hours%20of%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVaisberg%2C%20who's%20VC%20investing%20is%20focused%20on%20what%20he%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bmental%20fitness%26quot%3B%20space%2C%20said%20founders%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20would%20benefit%20from%20the%20understanding%20they%20get%20of%20themselves%20and%20how%20they%20can%20become%20better%20leaders%20by%20becoming%20more%20attuned%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20others.%20He%20could%20see%20VCs%20even%20recommending%20founders%20take%20part%20in%20ayahuasca%20ceremonies%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0even%20though%20there's%20a%20slight%20risk%20leaders%20could%20discover%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20doing%20what%20they're%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20with%20ayahuasca%20and%20the%201heart%20program%20has%20made%20Vaisberg%20more%20willing%20to%20trust%20his%20gut%2C%20which%20he%20didn't%20always%20do%20with%20past%20financial%20bets.%20%26quot%3BThose%20investments%20are%20not%20doing%20as%20well.%20And%20now%20I've%20learned%20to%20trust%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20instinct.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20do%20think%20from%20that%20perspective%2C%20it%20makes%20me%20a%20better%20investor.%20And%20from%20a%20founder%20perspective%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20all%20about%20human%20connection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychedelic-tea-ayahuasca-effects-founders-experiment-better-leaders-1heart-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701686881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a501e58e7c0c29a28f32a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychedelic-tea-ayahuasca-effects-founders-experiment-better-leaders-1heart-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20venture%20capitalist%20who%20recently%20tried%C2%A0ayahuasca%20thinks%20founders%20should%20consider%20using%20the%20psychedelic%20drink%20as%20a%20way%20to%20become%20better%20leaders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A