emselves%20were%20%E2%80%9Czip%20tied%2C%20shuffled%20around%2C%20and%20held%20in%20a%20room%2C%E2%80%9D%20while%20their%20presence%20did%20nothing%20to%20protect%20Palestinians%20from%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2023-10-21%2Fty-article-magazine%2F.premium%2Fbeatings-burns-attempted-sexual-assault-settlers-and-soldiers-abused-palestinians%2F0000018b-530f-d1d7-ab8b-7f5fca1d0000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etorture%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20attempted%20sexual%20assault.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20situation%20represents%20a%20new%20level%20of%20violence%20that%20we%20are%20not%20used%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20Eisner%20said.%20Sahar%20Vardi%2C%20an%20Israeli%20activist%20from%20South%20Hebron%20Hills%20said%20that%20since%20October%207%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20level%20of%20risk%20in%20doing%20protective%20presence%20is%20growing%2C%20and%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20protective%20presence%20is%20decreasing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08114729%2Fimage1170x530cropped-3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08114729%2Fimage1170x530cropped-3.jpg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08114729%2Fimage1170x530cropped-3-300x136.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08114729%2Fimage1170x530cropped-3-1024x464.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684057%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20night-time%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%20City%20by%20Israel.%20Photo%3A%20UNICEF%2FEyad%20El%20Baba%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%2