C%20suggesting%20that%20regional%20parties%20must%20lead%20the%20fight%20against%20BJP%20in%20areas%20they%20hold%20sway%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20won%20Telangana.%20They%20would%20have%20won%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Some%20votes%20were%20cut%20by%20INDIA%20parties.%20This%20is%20the%20truth.%20We%20had%20said%20suggested%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement.%20They%20lost%20because%20of%20division%20of%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20said%20in%20an%20address%20to%20the%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlong%20with%20ideology%2C%20you%20need%20to%20have%20a%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%2C%20BJP%20won't%20come%20to%20power%20in%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20she%20said%2C%20will%20work%20together%20and%20rectify%20mistakes%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election%20next%20year.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20learn%20from%20the%20mistakes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20come%20after%20the%20Congress%20suffered%20defeats%20in%20three%20heartland%20states%20-%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20The%20party%20managed%20to%20win%20just%20one%20seat%20in%20Mizoram%20after%20contesting%20all%2040.%20Its%20sole%20consolation%20is%20a%20victory%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20round%20of%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20Congress%20and%20its%20INDIA%20allies%20had%20contested%20separately%20on%20many%20seats.%20This%2C%20many%20have%20pointed%20out%2C%20led%20to%20a%20division%20in%20votes%20and%20benefited%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20talks%20with%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20party%2C%20but%20the%20talks%20fell%20apart%20over%20seat-sharing.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20was%20leading%20Congress's%20campaign%2C%20dismissed%20a%20media%20query%20on%20the%20alliance%20talks%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3Bchoro%20Akhilesh%20Vakhilesh%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20remark%20sealed%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20alliance%20talks.%20%26quot%3BThe%20insulting%20words%20used%20for%20Akhileshji%20by%20Kamal%20Nathji%20is%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20Congress's%20loss.%20The%20Congress%20lost%20because%20of%20those%20undignified%20remarks%2C%26quot%3B%20Samajwadi%20Party%20spokesperson%20Manoj%20Yadav%20Kaka%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20election%20results%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20today%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20long%20battle.%20We%20have%20to%20prepare%20a%20lot%20to%20defeat%20a%20party%20like%20BJP.%20We%20have%20to%20fight%20their%20strategies%20with%20discipline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20back%20where%20we%20started%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20started%20on%20the%20point%20that%20we%20have%20to%20support%20the%20parties%20in%20the%20regions%20they%20are%20strong%20in.%20The%202024%20polls%20will%20be%20historic.%20There%20will%20be%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20trends%20pointed%20to%20Congress's%20impending%20defeats%20yesterday%2C%20INDIA%20allies%20had%20started%20criticising%20the%20main%20opposition%20party's%20decision%20not%20to%20fight%20the%20elections%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanata%20Dal-United's%20KC%20Tyagi%20said%20the%20Congress%20%26quot%3Bignored%20other%20INDIA%20parties%2C%20but%20was%20unable%20to%20win%20on%20its%20own%26quot%3B.%20Kerala%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20CPM%20leader%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20said%20that%20it%20was%20necessary%20to%20fight%20together%20while%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20said%20the%20outcome%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20polls%20would%20have%20been%20different%20had%20the%20Congress%20shared%20some%20seats%20with%20other%20constituents%20of%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20leader%20from%20a%20major%20Opposition%20party%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20it%20appeared%20that%20Congress%20was%20waiting%20for%20the%20poll%20results%20for%20greater%20bargaining%20powers%20within%20the%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20no%20meetings%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20a%20long%20time.%20The%20Congress%20did%20not%20want%20to%20meet.%20Perhaps%20they%20were%20waiting%20for%20the%20results%20to%20have%20greater%20bargaining%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20its%20gamble%20not%20paying%20off%2C%20the%20main%20Opposition%20party%20is%20now%20on%20the%20backfoot%20before%20the%20next%20meeting%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20this%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701685440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F30vs2e5_mamata-banerjee-sonia-rahul-gandhi-aug2018_625x300_01_August_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefeat-of-congress-not-the-people-mamata-banerjee-on-bjps-3-state-win-4632171%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20lost%20key%20assembly%20polls%20in%20three%20states%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20with%20INDIA%20members%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20today%2C%20stressing%20that%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bdefeat%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20not%20the%20people%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefeat-of-congress-not-the-people-mamata-banerjee-on-bjps-3-state-win-4632171%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefeat-of-congress-not-the-people-mamata-banerjee-on-bjps-3-state-win-4632171%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefeat-of-congress-