2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jonea%20Gordon%2C%20a%2035-year-old%20year%20data%20privacy%20program%20manager%20based%20in%20Philadelphia.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20data-privacy%20program%20manager%20with%20a%20background%20that%20includes%20roles%20at%20Meta%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Cruise.%20Transitioning%20from%20law%20to%20data%20privacy%20and%20income%20growth%20from%20%2490%2C000%20to%20over%20%24400%2C000%20in%20five%20years%20marks%20my%20journey%20in%20this%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20share%20my%20experiences%20on%20platforms%20such%20as%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoneagordonesq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjoneagordon_esq%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20I%20focus%20on%20informing%20and%20inspiring%20others%2C%20especially%20those%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flack-of-diversity-tech-industry-risks-customers-top-talent-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderrepresented%20groups%20in%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20emphasize%20that%20you%20can%20succeed%20in%20tech%20without%20a%20traditional%20tech%20background.%20Here's%20how%20I%20got%20where%20I%20am%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20I%20started%20my%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20graduated%20from%20law%20school%20in%202009%20and%20became%20a%20litigation%20attorney.%20I%20soon%20realized%20the%20mismatch%20between%20the%20demanding%20nature%20of%20legal%20work%20and%20my%20personal%20values%2C%20and%20I%20desired%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnews-today-november-18-work-life-balance-job-careers-remote-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20balanced%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Despite%20the%20prestige%20and%20potential%20success%20in%20law%2C%20I%20wanted%20both%20fulfillment%20and%20flexibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ventured%20into%20real%20estate%20with%20my%20networking%20skills%20and%20initially%20found%20success%20selling%20houses%20to%20lawyers%20in%20my%20network%2C%20but%20I%20soon%20felt%20the%20same%20dissatisfaction%20that%20I%20had%20in%20my%20legal%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20I%20was%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20my%20dream%20career%2C%20which%20led%20me%20back%20to%20law%2C%20but%20this%20time%20as%20a%20legal%20recruiter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20position%20was%20instrumental%20in%20expanding%20my%20network%20and%20exposing%20me%20to%20various%20career%20paths%2C%20including%20data%20privacy.%20I%20hadn't%20encountered%20this%20field%20in%20law%20school%20and%20was%20increasingly%20drawn%20to%20it%2C%20especially%20since%20my%20clients%20at%20the%20time%20demonstrated%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20privacy%20attorneys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20I%20pivoted%20to%20data%20privacy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20maternity%20leave%20in%202018%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20networking%20and%20conducting%20informational%20interviews%20with%20professionals%20in%20the%20data-privacy%20sector.%20These%20interactions%20were%20crucial%20in%20understanding%20the%20necessary%20skills%20and%20certifications%20for%20a%20career%20in%20this%20field.%20I%20also%20asked%20the%20university%20where%20I%20did%20my%20undergraduate%20if%20I%20could%20audit%20their%20data-privacy%20courses%20for%20free%2C%20which%20I%20then%20put%20on%20my%20CV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20role%20I%20secured%20was%20a%20consulting%20position%20with%20a%20starting%20salary%20of%20%2490%2C000%2C%20a%20cut%20from%20my%20previous%20recruitment%20earnings.%20But%20this%20move%20was%20strategic%20because%20I%20discovered%20the%20lucrative%20potential%20of%20data%20privacy%20in%20tech%2C%20which%20far%20exceeded%20my%20initial%20expectati