5%20women%20MLAs%2C%20at%2019%20out%20of%20the%20total%2090%20MLAs.%20This%20is%20the%20highest%20proportion%20of%20women%20the%20state%20has%20ever%20seen%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20at%2021%25%2C%20but%20is%20still%20far%20less%20that%20the%2033%25%20reservation%20the%20Bill%20would%20create.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20states%20fared%20even%20worse.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Flegislature%2Flegislature_state_vital_stats_%2FTS_MLA_Profile.pdf%5C%22%3ETelangana%3C%2Fa%3E%20elected%2010%20women%20MLAs%20of%20the%20total%20119%20this%20year%2C%20up%20from%20six%20in%202018.%20This%20means%208%25%20of%20the%20assembly%20will%20comprise%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Flegislature%2Flegislature_state_vital_stats_%2FMP_MLA_Profile.pdf%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20women%20contestants%20won%2027%20of%20the%20230%20seats%20in%20the%20assembly%20%E2%80%93%20putting%20their%20share%20in%20the%20house%20at%2011.7%25.%20The%20highest%20ever%20was%20in%202013%2C%20when%2030%20women%20were%20elected%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Flegislature%2Flegislature_state_vital_stats_%2FRJ_MLA_Profile.pdf%5C%22%3ERajasthan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20share%20of%20women%20MLAs%20has%20gone%20this%20time%20when%20compared%20to%20last%20time.%20While%20there%20were%2024%20women%20election%20in%202018%2C%20that%20number%20has%20fallen%20to%2020%20%E2%80%93%20or%2010%25%20%E2%80%93%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701684041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04152158%2FGALn98pbMAAFBeo.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-many-women-were-elected-as-mlas-on-december-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Only%20one%20of%20the%20four%20states%20where%20results%20were%20declared%20on%20Sunday%20%E2%80%93%20Chhattisgarh%20%E2%80%93%20has%20more%20than%2020%25%20women%20MLAs%2C%20at%2019%20out%20of%20the%20total%2090%20MLAs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-many-women-were-elected-as-mlas-on-december-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Karnataka%20Momentum%20Lost%2C%20Congress%20And%20INDIA%20Need%20New%20Narrative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20big%20takeaway%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20opposition%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20from%20the%20results%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20is%20that%20the%20post-Karnataka%20momentum%20is%20lost%2C%20or%20at%20least%20has%20taken%20a%20huge%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20only%20one%20state%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20victory%20in%20Karnataka%20in%20May%202023%2C%20gave%20the%20Congress%20a%20bounce%20and%20bolstered%20the%20opposition.%20The%20BJP%20seems%20to%20have%20snatched%20that%20with%20its%20emphatic%20victories%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20win%20for%20the%20Congress%20is%20just%20consolation%20in%20the%20broader%20national%20context.%20Even%20there%20the%20numbers%20for%20the%20Congress%20are%20just%20five%20more%20than%20the%20half-way%20mark%20-%2064%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20one%20for%20its%20ally.%20That%20is%20cause%20for%20nervousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20recent%20history%20of%20defections%20and%20governments%20being%20toppled%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20have%20to%20watch%20its%20back%20in%20Hyderabad.%20There%20is%20no%20room%20for%20any%20friction%20over%20the%20choice%20of%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20exactly%20why%20the%20party%20is%20in%20a%20hurry%20to%20stake%20its%20claim%20to%20form%20a%20government%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20the%20loss%20for%20the%20Congress%20nationally%20will%20reflect%20in%20the%20power%20equations%20within%20the%20INDIA%20grouping.%20Post-Karnataka%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20buoyed%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20the%20glue%20and%20the%20leading%20force%20in%20bringing%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20murmurs%20of%20unhappiness%20among%20strong%20regional%20players%20over%20the%20power%20equations.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20push%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20wasn't%20a%20collective%20decision%3B%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20was%20not%20convinced%20it%20was%20the%20right%20way%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%20could%20not%20come%20together%20for%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20and%20the%20acerbic%20language%20used%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Kamal%20Nath%20-%20the%20Congress's%20Chief%20Ministerial%20face%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20-%20were%20not%20exactly%20team-bonding%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20hindsight%2C%20the%20Congress%20could%20have%20publicly%20reprimanded%20Kamal%20Nath%20and%20put%20up%20a%20strong%20message%20against%20the%20slighting%20of%20allies.%20It%20should%20have%20sacrificed%20more%20of%20its%20interests%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20to%20accommodate%20allies%20and%20ensure%20the%20alliance%20was%20strengthened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20has%20already%20said%20the%20results%20show%20the%20need%20for%20collective%20leadership%20and%20consultation%20with%20senior%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20comments%20will%20gain%20strength%20and%20the%20Congress%20will%20now%20have%20to%20play%20an%20equal%20in%20the%20alliance.%20The%20results%20weaken%20its%20position%20considerably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20only%20a%20southern%20silver%20lining%20-%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%20will%20now%20control%20Bengaluru%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Chennai%20and%20Thiruvananthapuram.%20But%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20already%20forged%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20(JDS)%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20may%20look%20to%20pacts%20with%20parties%20like%20the%20BRS%2C%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20or%20even%20the%20TDP%20and%20its%20estranged%20ally%20AIADMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20alliances%20could%20be%20consequential%20in%202024.%20While%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%20and%20the%20Congress%20cannot%20take%20the%20southern%20story%20for%20granted%2C%20without%20a%20stronger%20narrative%20they%20can't%20even%20begin%20to%20script%20a%20story%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20for%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%2C%20regional%20allies%20will%20have%20to%20do%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20and%20the%20Congress%20needs%20to%20find%20a%20stronger%20narrative.%20State-specific%20narratives%20where%20it's%20taking%20the%20BJP%20head%20on%20without%20ignoring%20the%20smallest%20of%20small%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(TM%20Veeraraghav%20is%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701683640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fiso52iro_india-alliance_625x300_02_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkarnataka-momentum-lost-congress-and-india-need-new-narrative-4632367%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first%20big%20takeaway%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20opposition%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20from%20the%20results%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20is%20that%20the%20post-Karnataka%20momentum%20is%20lost%2C%20or%20at%20least%20has%20taken%20a%20huge%20hit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkarnataka-momentum-lost-congress-and-india-need-new-narrative-4632367%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkarnataka-momentum-lost-