ublic%20must%20adhere%20to%20the%20safety%20protocols%20provided.%20I%20also%20request%20that%20the%20public%20should%20not%20come%20out%20without%20essential%20needs%20until%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20storm%20subsides%2C%E2%80%9D%20Stalin%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20of%20trains%20and%20flights%20was%20also%20hampered%20by%20the%20rains%2C%20with%20the%20runway%20at%20Chennai%20airport%20scheduled%20to%20remain%20closed%20until%2011%20pm%20on%20Monday%20at%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701682059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04145600%2Fimage.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcyclone-michaung-heavy-rainfall-floods-chennai%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chennai%20city%20and%20its%20adjacent%20districts%20experienced%20substantial%20rainfall%20overnight%2C%20with%20Meenambakkam%20recording%20196%20mm%20and%20Nungambakkam%20receiving%20154.3%20mm%20in%20the%2024%20hours%20leading%20up%20to%205%3A30%20am%20this%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcyclone-michaung-heavy-rainfall-floods-chennai%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cyclone%20Michaung%3A%2033%20flights%20diverted%20from%20Chennai%20to%20Bengaluru%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701681598000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105726616%2Cimgsize-920946.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2F33-flights-diverted-from-chennai-to-bengaluru-due-to-cyclone-michaung-impact%2Farticleshow%2F105724986.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Officials%20from%20Bangalore%20International%20Airport%20Limited%20(BIAL)%2C%20which%20manages%20KIA%2C%20reported%20the%20diversion%20of%20both%20domestic%20and%20international%20flights%2C%20including%20those%20operated%20by%20Indigo%2C%20Sp