.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20Became%20Shivraj%20Chouhan's%20Masterstroke%20In%20Election%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20BJP%20swept%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20election%2C%20the%20result%20flying%20in%20the%20face%20of%20exit%20poll%20predictions%2C%20the%20spotlight%20is%20on%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government's%20welfare%20schemes%20such%20as%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20that%20helped%20BJP%20tap%20into%20women%20votes%20and%20swung%20the%20polls%20in%20its%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20scheme%2C%20aimed%20at%20making%20women%20financially%20independent%2C%20is%20being%20considered%20a%20masterstroke%20by%20the%20four-time%20chief%20minister%20that%20helped%20BJP%20seal%20the%20victory%20in%20the%20heartland%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fpbqfhrao_shivraj-chouhan_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Scheme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mukhya%20Mantri%20Ladli%20Behna%20Scheme%20was%20launched%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Chouhan%20in%20March%20this%20year.%20Under%20the%20scheme%2C%20women%20in%20the%2023-60%20years%20age%20group%20receive%20Rs%201%2C000%20every%20month%20in%20their%20bank%20accounts.%20This%20amount%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%2C%20will%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20gradually.%20The%20objective%20is%20to%20make%20women%20self-reliant%20and%20also%20empower%20them%20to%20address%20their%20health%20and%20nutrition%20requirements%20by%20providing%20them%20financial%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho's%20Eligible%2C%20Who's%20Not%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarried%20women%20residents%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20the%2023-60%20years%20age%20group%20are%20eligible%20to%20avail%20the%20scheme's%20benefit.%20This%20includes%20widows%2C%20divorced%20and%20abandoned%20women%2C%20according%20to%20the%20scheme's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20from%20families%20with%20an%20annual%20income%20more%20than%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20are%20not%20eligible%20for%20the%20scheme's%20benefits.%20Women%20who%20are%20income%20tax%20payers%20or%20whose%20family%20members%20are%20government%20employees%20are%20also%20ineligible.%20Unmarried%20women%20cannot%20avail%20of%20the%20scheme%20either.%20Women%20whose%20family%20members%20are%20elected%20public%20representatives%20cannot%20avail%20the%20benefits.%20If%20a%20woman%20is%20already%20receiving%20an%20amount%20less%20than%20Rs%201%2C000%20under%20any%20other%20scheme%2C%20the%20difference%20will%20be%20paid%20to%20her%20under%20the%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20scheme.%20The%20scheme%20also%20stands%20out%20because%20the%20monthly%20instalments%20would%20only%20get%20deposited%20in%20her%20account%20and%20not%20that%20of%20her%20husband%20or%20any%20other%20relative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fige9sgu_ladli-behna_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Implementation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2040-member%20team%20involved%20in%20implementing%20the%20scheme%20pulled%20off%20a%20Herculean%20task%20by%20registering%201.25%20crore%20women%20under%20the%20scheme%20and%20crediting%20the%20assistance%20monthly%20in%2099%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20accounts%2C%20all%20within%20just%20100%20days.%20This%20was%20achieved%20through%20hundreds%20of%20camps%20set%20up%20for%20the%20registration.%20There%20would%20be%20long%20queues%2C%20but%20the%20process%20would%20take%20just%20minutes%2C%20even%20in%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C