%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Congress%20announced%20a%20monthly%20assistance%20of%20Rs%201%2C500%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20tweaked%20the%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20policy%20and%20hiked%20the%20monthly%20amount%20to%20Rs%201%2C250.%20Chief%20Minister%20Chouhan%20also%20said%20this%20amount%20would%20be%20increased%20gradually%20and%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Mukhya%20Mantra%20Ladli%20Behna%20Yojana%20has%20started%20with%20Rs%201%2C000%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20stop%20there.%20Your%20brother%20will%20keep%20increasing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chouhan%20then%20said.%20Congress's%20Kamal%20Nath%20had%20then%20said%20this%20was%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20save%20its%20%26quot%3Bsinking%20ship%26quot%3B%20and%20stressed%20that%20it%20won't%20work%2C%20but%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20confident.%20Even%20a%20day%20after%20the%20election%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20said%20the%20scheme%20was%20removing%20all%20thorns%20from%20the%20BJP's%20way%20to%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20Worked%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme's%20launch%20could%20be%20a%20political%20move%20in%20a%20poll%20year.%20But%20it%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20why%20it's%20crucial%20in%20a%20state%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20why%20it%20could%20potentially%20swing%20women%20votes.%20According%20to%20National%20Health%20and%20Family%20Survey%20data%2C%2023%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20in%20the%2015-49%20years%20age%20group%20have%20a%20body%20mass%20index%20lower%20than%20normal.%20Nearly%2055%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20in%20this%20age%20group%20are%20anaemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20about%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20in%20the%20state%20own%20house%2Fland%20individually%20or%20jointly.%20Only%2038.5%20women%20in%20the%20state%20have%20a%20mobile%20phone%20of%20their%20own.%20The%20number%20of%20women%20in%20the%20state's%20workforce%2C%20both%20in%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas%2C%20are%20also%20dismal.%20Against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20a%20scheme%20that%20puts%20money%20in%20their%20hands%20can%20potentially%20help%20them%20better%20care%20of%20themselves.%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20also%20ensured%20that%20the%20amount%20did%20not%20go%20to%20a%20male%20relative%20-%20a%20system%20that%20has%20often%20been%20misused.%20The%20scheme%20worked%20for%20women%20and%2C%20as%20the%20results%20showed%2C%20for%20the%20BJP%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701681060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fnj1h9lqg_ladli-behna_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivraj-singh-chouhan-ladli-behna-madhya-pradesh-election-2023-why-ladli-behna-became-shivraj-chouhans-masterstroke-in-election-year-4632153%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20BJP%20swept%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20election%2C%20the%20result%20flying%20in%20the%20face%20of%20exit%20poll%20predictions%2C%20the%20spotlight%20is%20on%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government's%20welfare%20schemes%20such%20as%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20that%20helped%20BJP%20tap%20into%20women%20votes%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivraj-singh-chouhan-ladli-behna-madhya-pradesh-election-2023-why-ladli-behna-became-shivraj-chouhans-masterstroke-in-election-year-4632153%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivraj-singh-chouhan-ladli-behna-madhya-pradesh-election-2023-why-ladli-behna-became-shivraj-chouhans-masterstroke-in-election-year-4632153%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivraj-singh-chouhan-ladli-behna-madhya-pradesh-election-2023-why-ladli-behna-became-shivraj-chouhans-masterstroke-in-election-year-4632153%2Famp