unting%20of%20votes%2C%20like%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20four%20states%20that%20voted%20in%20November%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fec-changes-counting-date-for-mizoram-assembly-polls-to-december-4%5C%22%3Erevise%20the%20date%20to%20December%204%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20poll%20panel%20received%20multiple%20representations%20from%20political%20parties%2C%20the%20Church%20and%20civil%20society%20organisations%20as%20December%203%20was%20a%20Sunday%2C%20the%20holy%20day%20for%20Christians%2C%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%E2%80%99s%20win%20in%20three%20North%20Indian%20states%20and%20the%20Congress%20taking%20Telangana%20on%20December%203%20has%20already%20set%20the%20tone%20in%20the%20media%20for%20election-related%20deliberations%20and%20stock-taking%2C%20the%20sweep%20of%20ZPM%20in%20a%20tiny%20state%20like%20Mizoram%20is%20also%20noteworthy.%20Here%20are%20eight%20takeaways%20from%20today%E2%80%99s%20Mizoram%20electoral%20results.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20ZPM%E2%80%99s%20win%20means%20Mizoram%20will%20get%20a%20new%20face%20as%20its%20chief%20minister%20in%20Lalduhoma.%20It%20can%20also%20mean%2079-year-old%20Zoramthanga%2C%20a%20stalwart%20in%20Mizo%20politics%20for%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20sailing%20off%20into%20the%20political%20sunset.%20Already%2C%20another%20veteran%20Mizo%20politician%2C%20former%20two-time%20chief%20minister%20Lalthanhawla%2C%20had%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20politics%20after%20the%202018%20loss%20of%20his%20Congress%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Today%E2%80%99s%20gigantic%20win%20by%20ZPM%20has%20also%20changed%20the%2035-year-old%20cycle%20of%20MNF%20and%20Congress%20sharing%20power%20in%20the%20border%20state%20alternately.%20After%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20Mizo%20Accord%20with%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201986%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20under%20Lalthanhawla%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20to%20give%20way%20to%20MNF%E2%80%99s%20Laldenga.%20Since%20then%2C%20in%20every%20assembly%20poll%2C%20the%20national%20party%20has%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20two-corner%20contest%20with%20the%20MNF%20until%20the%20ZPM%20arrived%20on%20the%20scene%20in%20the%202018%20polls%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20upped%20its%20game%20under%20Narendra%20Modi.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20the%20MNF%20failing%20to%20repeat%20its%202018%20win%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20regional%20party%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20break%20the%20cycle%20in%20Mizoram%20of%20a%20party%20failing%20to%20return%20to%20power%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term.%20It%20is%20no%20cakewalk%20for%20any%20party%20to%20sidestep%20anti-incumbency%20and%20return%20to%20power%20for%20a%20third%20term.%20In%20the%20Northeast%2C%20only%20the%20Congress%20under%20the%20chief%20ministership%20of%20Tarun%20Gogoi%20could%20pull%20it%20off%20in%20Assam%20in%202011.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29124850%2FF05qfKDacAAHNnr.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29124850%2FF05qfKDacAAHNnr.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29124850%2FF05qfKDacAAHNnr-300x151.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29124850%2FF05qfKDacAAHNnr-1024x514.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29124850%2FF05qfKDacAAHNnr-800x400.jpeg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677473%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22602%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMizoram%20chief%20minister%20Zoramthanga.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%20%2F%40ZoramthangaCM%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20December%204%20election%20results%20that%20threw%20up%20two%20wins%20for%20the%20BJP%20have%20underlined%20that%20its%20footprint%20in%20Mizoram%20is%20growing.%20However%2C%20it%20also%20holds%20up%20that%2C%20once%20again%2C%20the%20national%20party%20failed%20to%20have%20an%20MLA%20in%20the%20state%20from%20the%20majority%20Mizo%20community.%20This%20was%20even%20after%20the%20assembly%20speaker%20from%20the%20MNF%2C%20Lalrinliana%2C%20had%20shifted%20base%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20these%20elections.%20This%20makes%20Mizoram%20the%20only%20state%20where%20BJP%20has%20failed%20to%20enter%20a%20north-eastern%20state%E2%80%99s%20majority%20community%20in%20spite%20of%20being%20in%20power%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20In%20all%2C%20the%20BJP%20contested%2023%20seats.%20Only%20five%20of%20its%20candidates%20were%20non-Mizos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Today%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20has%20also%20shown%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Mara%20community%20has%20further%20firmed%20up.%20While%20the%20party%20candidate%20K.%20Hrahmo%20won%20the%20Palak%20seat%2C%20K.%20Beichhua%2C%20a%20former%20senior%20minister%20of%20the%20MNF%20who%20also%20recently%20moved%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20picked%20up%20the%20Siaha%20seat%20for%20the%20party.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20two%20wins%20for%20the%20BJP%20came%20soon%20after%20its%20sweep%20of%20the%20Mara%20District%20Council%20in%20Mizoram.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20Mara%20Democratic%20Front%20merged%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20gave%20the%20national%20party%20a%20much-needed%20entry%20into%20the%20Mara%20community%2C%20the%20second%20most%20influential%20community%20after%20the%20Mizos.%20In%202019%2C%20that%20move%20helped%20the%20BJP%20grab%20the%20Mara%20District%20Council.%20This%20past%20April%2C%20the%20BJP%20swept%20the%20Council%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20BJP%20losing%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcan-the-bjp-emerge-as-kingmaker-in-mizoram-as-pollsters-predict-a-hung-assembly%5C%22%3ETuichawng%20constituency%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20hold%20in%202018%20over%20the%20Chakma%20community%20in%20Mizoram%20was%20most%20likely%20due%20to%20the%20popularity%20of%20its%20then-candidate%20Budha%20Dhan%20Chakma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBudha%20Dhan%20Chakma%2C%20a%20former%20minister%20in%20the%20Lalthanhawla%20government%2C%20had%20moved%20to%20the%20BJP%20close%20to%20the%202018%20elections%20and%20went%20on%20to%20give%20the%20party%20its%20first%20taste%20of%20victory%20in%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20assembly%20elections.%20This%20time%20around%2C%20Budha%20Dhan%20had%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20politics%2C%20leading%20the%20BJP%20to%20bank%20on%20a%20new%20candidate%2C%20Durjya%C2%A0%20Dhan%20Chakma.%20He%20lost%20to%20MNF%E2%80%99s%20Rasik%20Mohan%20Chakma.%20Like%20in%20the%20Mara%20Council%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20also%20succeeded%20in%20capturing%20the%20Chakma%20District%20Council%20of%20Mizoram%2C%20a%20strategy%20it%20had%20adopted%20some%20years%20ago%20to%20enter%20the%20Mizoram%20election%20fray.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20recent%20polls%2C%20today%E2%80%99s%20winner%20from%20the%20MNF%2C%20Rasik%20Mohan%20Chakma%2C%20became%20its%20chief%20executive%20member.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20MNF%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20power%20also%20means%20that%20the%20Mizos%20did%20not%20consider%20the%20ethnic%20strife%20in%20Manipur%20that%20had%20affected%20their%20kindred%20community%2C%20the%20Kukis%2C%20as%20an%20election%20issue.%20The%20voters%20rather%20bit%20into%20the%20ZPM%E2%80%99s%20stand%20during%20the%20campaigning%20that%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20is%20important%20to%20all%20Zo%20people%20and%20their%20politicians%20across%20party%20lines.%20Though%20Zoramthanga%20had%20stridently%20batted%20for%20the%20Kukis%2C%20and%20also%20for%20the%20displaced%20Chins%20of%20Myanmar%2C%20and%20tried%20tilting%20it%20into%20an%20election%20issue%2C%20the%20voters%20didn%E2%80%99t%20look%20at%20him%20as%20the%20only%20Mizo%20leader%20who%20can%20continue%20that%20support%20to%20their%20kindred%20lot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Finally%2C%20while%20ZPM%E2%80%99s%20win%20has%20meant%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20new%20regional%20party%20in%20Mizoram%20after%20the%20MNF%2C%20the%20phenomenon%20is%2C%20but%2C%20only%20a%20second%20across%20the%20Northeast%20in%20recent%20times.%20In%20the%20last%20Nagaland%20elections%2C%20one%20saw%20a%20new%20regional%20party%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Democratic%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(NDPP)%2C%20seizing%20power%20from%20an%20already%20entrenched%20regional%20entity%2C%20the%20Naga%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20(NPF).%20Like%20the%20MNF%2C%20the%20NPF%20was%20also%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20first%20regional%20party%20to%20have%20grabbed%20power%20from%20the%20Congress%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20national%20party%20being%20well%20entrenched%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20in%20most%20of%20the%20Northeast.%20Like%20the%20MNF%2C%20the%20NPF%20was%20also%20a%20BJP%20ally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20NPF%2C%20ditto%20MNF%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20had%20resisted%20sharing%20power%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20the%20NDPP%E2%80%99s%20win%20in%20Nagaland%20made%20way%20for%20the%2