ews%2Fcyclone-michaung-chennai-rain-watch-flights-grounded-as-rainwater-enters-chennai-airport-runway-4631918%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fchennai-news%2Fcyclone-michaung-chennai-rain-watch-flights-grounded-as-rainwater-enters-chennai-airport-runway-4631918%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20%26quot%3BModi%20Ki%20Guarantee%26quot%3B%20Is%20The%20BJP's%20Warranty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20triumph%20and%20the%20Congress's%20inability%20to%20hold%20its%20ground%20in%20the%20heartland%20marked%20the%20state%20election%20results.%20The%20BJP%20looks%20poised%20for%20a%20hat%20trick%20in%202024.%20Narendra%20Modi%20may%20well%20equal%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20record%20of%20three%20successive%20general%20election%20wins.%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20begun%20chanting%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BAbki%20baar%2C%20400%20paar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(next%20time%2C%20400%20plus%20seats)%26quot%3B%2C%20hoping%20that%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20record%20of%20414%20seats%20in%201984%20will%20be%20surpassed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20Telangana%20revival%20notwithstanding%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20contend%20with%20the%20sarcasm%20of%20its%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20when%20they%20converge%20at%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20home%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20Trinamool%20Congress%20jibe%20at%20what%20it%20calls%20the%20Congress's%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ezamindari%3C%2Fem%3E%20attitude%26quot%3B%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20swipe%20about%20Congress%20%26quot%3Barrogance%26quot%3B%20have%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20an%20awkward%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20is%20unlikely%20to%20let%20go%20of%20Kamal%20Nath's%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BAkhilesh-Wakhilesh%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20sarcasm%20when%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20sought%20a%20seat%20sharing%20deal%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Though%20NCP%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%20sounded%20optimistic%20about%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Congress%20hope%20that%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20state%20polls%20or%20%26quot%3Bsemi-final%20to%202024%26quot%3B%20would%20place%20it%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%20has%20bombed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20there%20is%20a%20wedding%20in%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20family%20in%20Darjeeling.%20Apparently%2C%20while%20picking%20a%20date%20for%20the%20INDIA%20meeting%2C%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20consult%20its%20alliance%20partners.%20The%20party%20may%20stand%20with%20Trinamool%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20when%20the%20Ethics%20panel%20tables%20its%20report%20in%20parliament%20in%20the%20cash%20for%20query%20row%2C%20but%20coordinating%20meeting%20dates%20with%20allies%20is%20apparently%20something%20the%20party%20does%20not%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20said%2C%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BEk%20akela%20kitno%20par%20bhari%3C%2Fem%3E%20(One%20alone%20can%20take%20on%20so%20many)%26quot%3B.%20Sunday's%20outcome%20underscored%20the%20theme.%20Modi%20described%20the%20mandate%20as%20the%20defeat%20of%20the%20politics%20of%20dynasty%20and%20appeasement.%20Tossing%20aside%20the%20Congress'%20campaign%20for%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20the%20PM%20reiterated%2C%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bclass%20and%20not%20caste%26quot%3B%20that%20unites.%20He%20identifies%20women%2C%20youth%2C%20farmers%20and%20the%20poor%2C%20cutting%20across%20caste%20lines%2C%20as%20the%20four%20%26quot%3Bcastes%26quot%3B%2C%20emphasising%20that%20OBCs%20are%20part%20of%20each%20of%20the%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20religious%20rhetoric%3B%20with%20its%20Hindutva%20baseline%20intact%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20now%20targeting%20welfare%20and%20governance%20beyond%20religiosity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20%3Cem%3Eki%3C%2Fem%3E%20guarantee%26quot%3B%20-%20the%20term%20was%20first%20used%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20while%20inaugurating%20the%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20in%20Delhi%20on%20July%2026%20-%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20BJP's%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victory%20celebration%20at%20the%20BJP%20national%20headquarters%20was%20symbolic.%20A%20banner%20on%20the%20stage%20from%20where%20BJP%20chief%20Jagat%20Prakash%20Nadda%20and%20Modi%20addressed%20workers%20declared%20in%20boldface%3A%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BSapne%20nahin%2C%20haqeeqat%20bante%20hain%3B%20tabhi%20toh%20sab%20Modi%20ko%20chahte%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Not%20just%20dreams%2C%20he%20shapes%20reality.%20That%20is%20why%20everyone%20wants%20Modi)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20symbolic%20in%20a%20way.%20It%20was%20held%20at%20the%20new%20extension%20building%20of%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20at%20Deen%20Dayal%20Upadhyay%20Marg%20(the%20road%2C%20formerly%20Rouse%20Avenue%2C%20was%20renamed%20in%20the%201970s%20when%20BJP's%20precursor%20Jana%20Sangh%20ruled%20the%20local%20administration%20of%20Delhi).%20The%20BJP%20built%20its%20new%20office%20after%202014%20and%20now%20is%20expanding%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20next%20door%20stands%20the%20unfinished%20structure%20of%20an%20office%20the%20Congress%20started%20building%20much%20earlier.%20(In%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20era%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20with%20the%20active%20cooperation%20of%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%2C%20then%20controlled%20by%20Ambanis%2C%20had%20built%20the%20magnificent%20Jawahar%20Bhavan%20next%20to%20the%20parliament%20complex%20to%20house%20its%20offices.%20It%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20family-controlled%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Foundation).%20The%20Congress%20is%20struggling%20to%20set%20its%20house%20in%20order%20while%20the%20BJP%20expands.%20Resources%20are%20not%20a%20constraint.%20Decisiveness%20and%20coherence%20are%20sorely%20lacking%20in%20India's%20oldest%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20is%20not%20lost%20for%20the%20Congress%20though.%20Its%20victory%20in%20Telangana%20has%20made%20the%20BJP's%20bid%20for%20a%20%26quot%3BCongress%20%3Cem%3Emukt%3C%2Fem%3E%20Bharat%20(Congress-free%20India)%26quot%3B%20a%20distant%20dream.%20After%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20victory%20in%20Telangana%20has%20given%20the%20beleaguered%20party%20a%20reason%20to%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP's%20majority%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20is%20comfortable%2C%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20in%20Telangana%20saw%20the%20Congress%20rush%20to%20the%20Governor%20in%20Hyderabad%20to%20stake%20its%20claim%20to%20power%20on%20Sunday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20victorious%20Congress%20MLAs%20in%20Telangana%20defected%20from%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20or%20KCR's%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS).%20Apparently%2C%20there%20are%20concerns%20within%20the%20Congress%20about%20the%20durability%20of%20its%20slender%20majority%2C%20which%20compelled%20the%20party%20to%20rush%20to%20Raj%20Bhavan.%20The%20Congress's%20Telangana%20chief%20A%20Revanth%20Reddy%20-%20tipped%20to%20be%20Chief%20Minister%20-%20began%20his%20career%20in%20the%20BJP-linked%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP).%20He%20traversed%20to%20the%20Congress%20via%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20BRS%20(then%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi).%20Given%20the%20fragility%20of%20the%20Telangana%20polity%2C%20where%20party%20loyalties%20keep%20shifting%2C%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20decided%20not%20to%20take%20chances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20prior%20to%20Sunday's%20counting%20of%20votes%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20emboldened%20by%20the%20exit%20polls%20and%20media%20projections%2C%20announced%20state%20observers%20for%20all%20four%20states%2C%20to%20oversee%20post-poll%20government-making.%20Of%20these%2C%20only%20the%20team%20assigned%20to%20Hyderabad%20(headed%20by%20Karnataka's%20DK%20Shiva%20Kumar%2C%20who%20has%20the%20ability%20and%20wherewithal%20to%20handle%20political%20fragility)%20has%20any%20work%20to%20do.%20The%20other%20teams%20may%20now%20oversee%20the%20election%20of%20Leaders%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20Raipur%20and%20Bhopal.%20The%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20name%20observers%20for%20post-poll%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20won%20the%20trophy%20in%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Man%20of%20the%20Match%20belongs%20to%20the%20BJP%20-%20Katipally%20Venkata%20Ramana%20Reddy.%20He%20has%20been%20dubbed%20the%20double%20giant%20killer%20after%20defeating%20both%20incumbent%20Chief%20Minister%20KCR%20(BRS)%20and%20chief%20ministerial%20probable%20Revanth%20Reddy%20(Congress)%20at%20Kamareddy.%20(KCR%20and%20Revanth%20Reddy%20won%20their%20second%20seats).%20The%20BJP%20finished%20third%20in%20this%20southern%20state.%20However%20its%20vote%20percentage%20has%20doubled%20from%20seven%20in%202018%20(one%20seat)%20to%2014%20(eight%20seats).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20takeaway%20from%20Telangana%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20Congress's%20surge%2C%20is%20the%20eclipse%20of%20a%20regional%20party.%20Does%20the%20Telangana%20result%20have%20a%20message%20for%20the%20future%20in%20other%20states%20where%20national%20parties%20have%20been%20on%20the%20back%20foot%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20sending%20MPs%20to%20contest%20as%20MLAs%2C%20the%20BJP%20perhaps%20initiated%20a%20%26quot%3BKamraj%20Plan%26quot%3B%20-%20the%20Congress%20strategy%20of%201963%20to%20revamp%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20saw%20the%20intransigence%20of%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20while%20candidates%20were%20chosen%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20the%20stubbornness%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20even%20resulted%20in%20an%20INDIA%20rally%20in%20Bhopal%20being%20called%20off%20weeks%20after%20it%20was%20announced%20with%20fanfare%20when%20the%20alliance%20last%20met%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20rejuvenated%20BJP%20will%20take%20on%20a%20confused%20INDIA%20alliance.%20The%20December%203%20results%20may%20be%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise%20for%20INDIA%20parties%20who%20were%20never%20comfortable%20with%20accepting%20Congress%20as%20the%20dominant%20partner.%20Despite%20its%20defeat%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20remain%20the%20Gandhi%20family's%20fiefdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201980%2C%20when%20OBC%20politics%2C%20which%20has%20lately%20emerged%20as%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20leitmotif%2C%20was%20at%20its%20peak%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20countered%2C%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BNa%20jaat%20par%20na%20paat%20par%2C%20Indiraji%20ki%20baat%20par%2C%20mohar%20lagegi%20haath%20par%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Not%20on%20caste%2C%20but%20on%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20word%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20win%20votes)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20%3Cem%3Eki%3C%2Fem%3E%20guarantee%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20slogan%20against%20castiest%20politics%2C%20perhaps%20in%20a%20similar%20vein.%20From%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BModi%20hai%20toh%20mumkin%20hai%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20moved%20on%20to%20%26quot%3BModi%20%3Cem%3Ehai%20toh%3C%2Fem%3E%20guarantee%20%3Cem%3Ehai%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20as%20its%20battlecry%20for%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20when%20a%20book%20to%20commemorate%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%2050%20years%20in%20legislative%20politics%20was%20launched%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20there%20was%20an%20undercurrent%20that%20suggested%20that%20Kharge%20is%20the%20face%20against%20Modi%20for%202024.%20Be%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20the%20battle%20lines%20for%202024%20seem%20decisively%20skewed%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701678780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fphdednj8_modi-ani_625x300_04_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmodi-ki-guarantee-is-the-bjps-warranty-4631455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP's%20triumph%20and%20the%20Congress's%20inability%20to%20hold%20its%20ground%20in%20the%20heartland%20marked%20the%20state%20election%20results.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmodi-ki-guarantee-is-the-bjps-warranty-4631455%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmodi-ki-guarantee-is-the-bjps-warranty-4631455%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmodi-ki-guarantee-is-the-bjps-warranty-4631455%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Crimes%20Against%20Women%20and%20Children%2C%20Suicides%2C%20Sudden%20Deaths%20Increased%20in%202022%3A%20NCRB%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F18224008%2Fmax-kleinen-ugdKmhDg1m8-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20released%20the%20annual%20crime%20report%2C%20and%20the%20Accidental%20Deaths%20and%20Suicides%20in%20India%20(ADSI)%20report%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%C2%A0December%203%2C%20when%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20four%20states%20were%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20it%20was%20published%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcrimes-against-women-children-scst-and-cyber-crimes-increased-in-2022-crime-in-india-report%2Farticle67602315.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20report%20provides%20a%20comprehensive%20overview%20of%20the%20crime%20scenario%20in%20India%20in%202022%2C%20including%20the%20number%20of%20sudden%20deaths%2C%20suicides%2C%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20children%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20crime%20rate%20declined%20from%207%25%20in%202021%20to%206.9%25%20in%202022%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported%2C%20citing%20the%20NCRB%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20crimes%20against%20specific%20categories%2C%20including%20women%2C%20children%2C%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20and%20cyber%20crimes%2C%20increased%20compared%20to%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESudden%20deaths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20an%2011.6%25%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20%E2%80%9Csudden%20deaths%E2%80%9D%20reported%20across%20the%20country%2C%20the%20ADSI%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2056%2C653%20sudden%20deaths%20were%20reported%20in%202022%2C%20with%20heart%20attacks%20accounting%20for%2032%2C410%20deaths.%20Other%20reasons%20were%20attributed%20for%2024%2C243%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20age%20group%20of%2045-60%20years%20reported%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20deaths%20(19%2C456).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20study%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20and%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmagazines%2Fpanache%2Fcardiovascular-diseases-killing-indians-the-most-pulmonary-embolism-rheumatic-condition-and-other-heart-disorders-people-should-know-about%2Farticleshow%2F94509483.cms%5C%22%3Eaccounts%20for%20approximately%2060%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20heart%20disease%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuicides%20and%20accidental%20deaths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuicides%20increased%20to%201%2C70%2C924%20in%202022%20compared%20to%201%2C64%2C033%20in%202021%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccidental%20deaths%20also%20increased%20to%204%2C30%2C504%20in%202022%20compared%20to%203%2C97%2C530%20in%202021%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fdata-gaps%2Fis-indias-highest-suicide-rate-because-of-better-reporting-or-rising-distress-836959%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FADSI-2021%2FADSI_2021_FULL_REPORT.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20highest%20suicide%20rate%20in%20its%20history%20in%202021%2C%20with%2012%20suicides%20for%20every%20100%2C000%20people.%20But%20the%20numbers%20could%20be%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202022%2C%20a%20psychiatrist%20had%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20there%20are%20several%20reasons%20why%20India%20might%20be%20underreporting%20suicides.%20These%20are%20lack%20of%20medical%20certification%20of%20deaths%2C%20stigma%20associated%20with%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20criminalisation%2C%20not%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20reporting%20of%20sucides%20but%20sometimes%20also%20in%20the%20denial%20of%20insurance%20if%20the%20death%20is%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrimes%20against%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%204%2C45%2C256%20cases%20of%20%E2%80%98crimes%20against%20women%E2%80%99%20were%20registered%20in%202022%2C%20showing%20a%204%25%20increase%20from%202021%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20cases%20included%20cruelty%20by%20husband%20or%20his%20relatives%2C%20kidnapping%20and%20abduction%20of%20women%2C%20assault%20on%20women%20with%20intent%20to%20outrage%20her%20modesty%2C%20and%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-62830634%5C%22%3E2022%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%2C%20said%20that%20one%20in%20three%20women%20globally%20face%20gender-based%20violence%20and%20the%20numbers%20for%20India%20are%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20noted%20that%20India%20recorded%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20ever%20in%202021.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20rise%20of%2026.35%25%20over%20six%20years%20since%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrimes%20against%20children%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%201%2C62%2C449%20cases%20of%20crimes%20against%20children%20were%20registered%20in%202022%2C%20reflecting%20an%208.7%25%20increase%20from%202021%2C%20the%20daily%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKidnapping%20and%20abduction%20and%20crimes%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act%20were%20prominent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20crimes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrimes%20against%20senior%20citizens%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%2C%20and%20economic%20offences%20showed%20a%20massive%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20total%20of%2028%2C545%20cases%20were%20registered%20for%20committing%20crimes%20against%20senior%20citizens%20(above%2060%20years)%2C%20showing%20an%20increase%20of%209.3%25%20over%202021%20(26%2C110%20cases)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20total%20of%2057%2C582%20cases%20were%20registered%20for%20committing%20crimes%20against%20SCs%2C%20showing%20an%20increase%20of%2013.1%25%20over%202021%20(50%2C900%20cases)%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20total%20of%2010%2C064%20cases%20were%20registered%20for%20committing%20crime%20against%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%2C%20showing%20an%20increase%20of%2014.3%25%20over%202021%20(8%2C802%20cases)%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%201%2C93%2C385%20cases%20were%20registered%20under%20economic%20offences%20%E2%80%93%20an%2011.1%25%20increase%20from%202021%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20cyber%20crimes%2C%2065%2C893%20cases%20were%20registered%2C%20showing%20a%2024.4%25%20increase%20in%20registration%20from%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%202022%2C%2064.8%25%20of%20the%20cyber%20crime%20cases%20registered%20were%20with%20the%20motive%20of%20fraud%20(42%2C710%20out%20of%2065%2C893%20cases)%20followed%20by%20extortion%20at%205.5%25%20(3%2C648%20cases)%2C%20and%20sexual%20exploitation%20at%205.2%25%20(3%2C434%20cases).%20A%20total%20of%205%2C610%20cases%20were%20registered%20in%202022%20as%20compared%20with%205%2C164%20cases%20in%20the%20year%202021%2C%20showing%20an%20increase%20of%208.6%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%205%2C610%20cases%2C%2078.5%25%20of%20cases%20were%20registered%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Damage%20to%20Public%20Property%20Act%20(4%2C403%20Cases)%20followed%20by%201%2C005%20(17.9%25)%20cases%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701678620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F18224008%2Fmax-kleinen-ugdKmhDg1m8-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcrimes-against-women-and-children-suicides-sudden-deaths-increased-in-2022-ncrb-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%204%2C45%2C256%20cases%20of%20'crimes%20against%20women'%20were%20registered%20in%202022%2C%20showing%20a%204%25%20increase%20from%202021.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcrimes-against-women-and-children-suicides-sudden-deaths-increased-in-2022-ncrb-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20A%20Big%20Fan%20Of...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-Ind%20Star's%20Blunt%20Take%20On%203%20Captains%20For%20SA%20Tour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%C2%A0(BCCI)%20announced%20three%20separate%20captains%20in%20the%20three%20formats%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20for%20the%20upcoming%20tour%20of%20South%20Africa.%20While%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20continue%20as%20the%20Test%20captain%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3