%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20youngest%20state%2C%20Telangana%2C%20has%20seen%20just%20one%20party%20at%20the%20helm%20since%20its%20birth%20in%202014%20-%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(formerly%20the%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samiti).%20But%20that%20will%20soon%20change%20as%20the%20Congress%20comprehensively%20defeated%20BRS%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20whose%20results%20were%20declared%20yesterday.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20won%2065%20seats%20in%20the%20119-member%20Telangana%20assembly%2C%20while%20the%20BRS%20got%20only%2039.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20party%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20candidate%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20an%20announcement%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%203%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20the%20fray%20to%20win%20the%20top%20post%20in%20Telangana%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevanth%20Reddy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy's%20style%20of%20functioning%20as%20Telangana%20Congress%20chief%20earned%20him%20several%20detractors%20within%20the%20party%20ranks%2C%20but%20the%2054-year-old%20marshalled%20his%20troops%20well%20enough%20to%20dethrone%20BRS%20in%20the%20southern%20state.%20The%20party%20fielded%20him%20against%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20in%20the%20elections%2C%20an%20indication%20of%20his%20rising%20stature%20within%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20appointment%20as%20Telangana%20Congress%20chief%20in%20July%202021%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20was%20increasingly%20visible%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20leading%20street%20protests%20on%20a%20host%20of%20issues%20against%20the%20ruling%20BRS%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhatti%20Vikramarka%20Mallu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20Legislature%20Party%20leader%20Mallu%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%20was%20another%20prominent%20face%20in%20Congress'%20intense%20campaign%20to%20oust%20KCR.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20polls%2C%20he%20had%20carried%20out%20a%201%2C400%20km%20padyatra%20across%20the%20state%2C%20not%20only%20to%20win%20voters%20but%20also%20to%20talk%20to%20them%20and%20understand%20their%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2062-year-old's%20'People's%20March'%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20ensuring%20the%20Congress'%20resurgence%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20was%20head%20of%20the%20Congress'%20Telangana%20unit%20till%20July%202021%2C%20when%20he%20was%20replaced%20by%20Revanth%20Reddy.%20But%20the%20leader%20is%20still%20quite%20popular%20among%20party%20workers%20in%20the%20state%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20names%20likely%20to%20be%20considered%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20party%20was%20heading%20for%20a%20win%20in%20the%20southern%20state%2C%20the%20leader%20said%20that%20he%20would%20be%20fine%20with%20any%20decision%20by%20the%20party's%20high%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701678360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fn47vv01k_telgana-cm-contenders_625x300_04_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelangana-chief-minister-announcement-soon-3-congress-leaders-in-the-fray-revanth-reddy-bhatti-vikramarka-mallu-4631452%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20youngest%20state%2C%20Telangana%2C%20has%20seen%20just%20one%20party%20at%20the%20helm%20since%20its%20birth%20in%202014%20-%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(formerly%20the%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samiti).%20But%20that%20will%20soon%20change%20as%20the%20Congress%20comprehensively%20defeated%20BRS.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelangana-chief-minister-announcement-soon-3-congress-leaders-in-the-fray-revanth-reddy-bhatti-vikramarka-mallu-4631452%22%2C%