egan%20strongly%20before%20being%20reduced%20to%20144%2F7%20in%2018%20overs.%20With%20the%20Aussies%20needing%2017%20runs%20from%2012%20balls%2C%20Mukesh%20Kumar%20gave%20away%20only%207%20runs%20in%20the%2019th%20over%2C%20before%20Arshdeep%2C%20who%20had%20conceded%2037%20runs%20in%20his%20first%20three%20overs%2C%20found%20his%20mojo%20to%20dismiss%20Matthew%20Wade%20and%20then%20seal%20the%20victory%20for%20the%20home%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Faustralia-in-india%2Findia-vs-australia-5th-t20i-arshdeep-singh-got-over-culprit-thoughts-to-deliver-a-match-winning-final-over%2Farticleshow%2F105721048.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%3A%20Caste-Based%20Violence%20in%20an%20Upper%20Primary%20School%20Exposes%20Deep-Rooted%20Discrimination%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04112831%2Fimage-1567.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20rainy%20September%20afternoon.%20Principal%20Anita%20Katiyar%20assembled%20the%20students%20of%20Sonepur%20Upper%20Primary%20school%2C%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Chitrakoot%20district%2C%20after%20lunchtime.%20It%20was%20brought%20to%20her%20attention%20that%20some%20students%20played%20in%20the%20rain%20and%20got%20drenched.%20This%20playful%20behaviour%20upset%20her%20to%20no%20end.%20She%20pulled%20the%20truants%20aside%20%E2%80%93%20class%208%20students%20Tara%20and%20her%20four%20girlfriends.%20Then%20she%20brought%20out%20a%20bamboo%20stick%20and%20beat%20the%20five%20drenched%20girls%20in%20front%20of%20the%20gathered%20students.%20She%20beat%20them%20till%20they%20were%20black%20and%20blue.%20Tara%20took%20the%20worst%20beating.%20Her%20arm%20was%20swollen%2C%20nose%20was%20bleeding%2C%20and%20her%20thighs%20were%20badly%20bruised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20understood%20why%20principal%20Katiyar%20got%20so%20angry.%20Yes%2C%20Tara%20and%20her%20friends%20got%20a%20little%20wet%20but%20who%20can%20resist%20a%20little%20dance%20in%20the%20first%20winter%20rains!%20The%20girls%20cried%20and%20howled%20and%20screamed%20but%20their%20principal%20did%20not%20stop%20thrashing%20them.%20Tara%20grabbed%20the%20bamboo%20stick%20from%20her%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20hands.%20Enraged%2C%20principal%20Katiyar%20snapped%20the%20cane%20into%20two%20and%20resumed%20the%20beating.%20Splinters%20flew%20into%20Tara%E2%80%99s%20face%20and%20bloodied%20her%20nose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20dare%20you%20%26lt%3B%3Cem%3Ethwack%3C%2Fem%3E%3E!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20think%20you%E2%80%99re%20my%20equal%20%26lt%3B%3Cem%3Ethwack%3C%2Fem%3E%3E!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20see%2C%20Tara%20Devi%20was%20a%20chamar%20%5BScheduled%20Caste%5D%20student%2C%20from%20the%20chamar%20%3Cem%3Ebasti%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Sonepur.%20So%20were%20her%20friends%20Anchal%20and%20Anjali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20may%20argue%20making%20everything%20about%20caste%2C%20so%20let%20me%20stop%20you%20right%20there%2C%20as%20this%20situation%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20%3Cem%3Ewas%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sonepur%2C%20Patels%20(or%20Kurmis%20and%20Katiyars)%20were%20numerous%20and%20dominant.%20They%20influenced%20almost%20everything%20in%20the%20village.%20It%20was%20not%20hard%20to%20guess%20why%20the%20chamar%20%3Cem%3Ebasti%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Sonepur%20had%20no%20%3Cem%3Epakka%3C%2Fem%3E%20roads%20or%20functional%20sewers%2C%20or%20why%20Katiyar%20remained%20at%20her%20post%20in%20Sonepur%20Upper%20Primary%20despite%20a%20long%20list%20of%20complaints%20compiled%20over%20a%20decade.%20Principal%20Katiyar%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20live%20in%20the%20village%2C%20but%20she%20was%20feared%20by%20chamar%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20we%20are%20told%2C%20a%20group%20of%20chamar%20students%20was%20forced%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school%20because%20of%20her%20violent%20temper.%20Some%20of%20them%20went%20to%20schools%20far%20away%20from%20their%20own%20village.%20Some%20never%20went%20to%20school%20again%2C%20like%20Prema%E2%80%99s%20little%20brother.%20He%20was%20in%20class%208%20when%20principal%20Katiyar%2C%20then%20only%20a%20senior%20teacher%2C%20ruthlessly%20beat%20him.%20He%20left%20the%20school%20suddenly%2C%20without%20even%20sitting%20for%20the%20final%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrincipal%20Katiyar%20was%20not%20just%20violent.%20She%20was%20an%20avowed%20casteist.%20It%20was%20her%20habit%20to%20make%20chamar%20students%20come%20early%20to%20school%20and%20sweep%20the%20floors%20and%20clean%20the%20toilets.%20She%20made%20them%20cut%20the%20grass%20in%20the%20school%20compound.%20She%20flatly%20refused%20to%20get%20on%20with%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20cooks%2C%20who%20were%20also%20chamar.%20The%20school%E2%80%99s%20most%20recent%20cook%2C%20Sangeeta%2C%20quit%20her%20job%20in%20a%20ragey%20huff%20when%20the%20principal%20hit%20her%20with%20the%20hot%20ladle%20she%20was%20using%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Katiyar%20was%20upset%20that%20a%20lowly%20chamar%20school%20cook%20could%20possess%20the%20latest%20touch%20screen%20smartphone.%20Suddenly%20short%20of%20a%20cook%2C%20the%20principal%20forced%20Tara%20and%20her%20chamar%20friends%20to%20cook%20midday%20meals%20for%20the%20whole%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20few%20concerned%20people%20brought%20these%20things%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20district%E2%80%99s%20Basic%20Shiksha%20Adhikari%20(BSA)%2C%20they%20calmly%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20part%20of%20our%20national%20cleanliness%20campaign.%20Children%20must%20take%20responsibility%20to%20keep%20their%20school%20clean.%E2%80%9D%20Is%20cleaning%20a%20job%20only%20for%20the%20chamar%20students%3F%20Are%20cooking%20school%20meals%20and%20cutting%20grass%20also%20part%20of%20this%20cleanliness%20drive%3F%20These%20questions%20remain%20unanswered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2020%2C%20when%20principal%20Katiyar%20was%20raining%20down%20blows%20on%20Tara%2C%20a%20few%20students%20ran%20to%20her%20%3Cem%3Ebasti%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20fetch%20her%20family%20members.%20%E2%80%9CGo%2C%20call%20whoever%20you%20want.%20Tell%20whoever%20you%20want%20to.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20principal%20Katiyar%20shouted.%20Minutes%20later%2C%20Tara%E2%80%99s%20mother%20Sumitra%20Devi%20and%20aunt%20Suneeta%20rushed%20to%20the%20school.%20Father%20Keshav%20stayed%20at%20home%3B%20he%20knew%20he%20would%20lose%20his%20temper%20and%20do%20something%20rash.%20Aunt%20Suneeta%20caught%20hold%20of%20principal%20Katiyar%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Edupatta%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20resist%20the%20attack%20on%20her%20niece.%20Later%2C%20the%20principal%20wrote%20to%20the%20BSA%2C%20lodging%20a%20complaint%20about%20aunt%20Suneeta.%20The%20report%20said%20that%20principal%20Katiyar%20was%20threatened%20in%20her%20own%20school%20and%20that%20she%20felt%20unsafe%20now%2C%20that%20too%20in%20her%20own%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMother%20Sumitra%20went%20to%20the%20police%20to%20lodge%20a%20complaint%20the%20next%20day%2C%20accompanied%20by%20the%20district%E2%80%99s%20social%20workers.%20Local%20reporters%20also%20came%2C%20to%20talk%20to%20Tara%2C%20Anchal%2C%20and%20Anjali%20and%20their%20families.%20The%20girls%20described%20the%20violence%20and%20talked%20about%20their%20principal%E2%80%99s%20discriminatory%20behaviour%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20reporters%20took%20videos%20of%20Tara%E2%80%99s%20injuries%20and%20wrote%20righteous%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20which%20became%20viral.%20In%20so%20many%20years%20of%20oppressive%20behaviour%2C%20no%20one%20had%20actually%20dared%20to%20report%20Katiyar%20to%20the%20authorities.%20This%20incident%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20become%20a%20national%20issue.%20Under%20pressure%2C%20principal%20Katiyar%20and%20the%20local%20police%20needed%20to%20take%20some%20visible%20action%20about%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20when%20justice%20seemed%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20things%20in%20Sonepur%20took%20a%20chilling%20but%20unsurprising%20turn.%20The%20local%20police%20brokered%20an%20inexplicable%20%3Cem%3Esamjhauta%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5Bdeal%5D%20between%20principal%20Katiyar%20and%20Tara%E2%80%99s%20family.%20These%20were%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20compromise%3A%201)%20all%20evidence%2C%20including%20videos%20and%20posts%2C%20taken%20by%20social%20workers%20and%20journalists%20will%20be%20deleted%3B%202)%20Tara%20will%20apologise%20to%20her%20principal%3B%203)%20the%20police%20complaint%20against%20principal%20Katiyar%20will%20be%20withdrawn%3B%204)%20principal%20Katiyar%20will%20file%20a%20complaint%20against%20Tara%E2%80%99s%20family%20for%20threatening%20her%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20this%20make%20sense%20to%20you%2C%20dear%20reader%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnable%20to%20comprehend%20the%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20social%20workers%20and%20journalists%20returned%20to%20Sonepur%20in%20search%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98truth%E2%80%99.%20Clouds%20of%20explanation%20were%20hovering%20all%20over%20the%20chamar%20%3Cem%3Ebasti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20each%20one%20more%20bizarre%20than%20the%20other.%20Tara%E2%80%99s%20father%20Keshav%20explained%20to%20everyone%20that%20principal%20Katiyar%20was%20a%20patient%20of%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20who%20was%20unfairly%20provoked%20by%20his%20daughter.%20When%20no%20one%20was%20listening%2C%20he%20muttered%20to%20himself%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20only%20poor%20labour%2C%20who%20are%20we%20to%20complain.%20I%20have%20other%20children%20whose%20futures%20I%20have%20to%20think%20about.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnchal%20and%20Anjali%2C%20Tara%E2%80%99s%20closest%20friends%20and%20fellow%20victims%20of%20the%20principal%E2%80%99s%20unrestrained%20violence%2C%20changed%20their%20statements%2