lectric%20IONIQ%205%20to%20none%20other%20than%20Bollywood%20superstar%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20who%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20the%20Korean%20carmaker%20as%20its%20brand%20ambassador%20since%2025%20years%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SAHIL%20KUKREJA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Felectric-cars%2Fshah-rukh-khan-takes-delivery-of-hyundai-ioniq-5-whats-special-about-this-rs-46-lakh-ev%2Farticleshow%2F105720301.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Does%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Revival%20of%20the%20CAA%20Issue%20Reflect%20the%20Party%E2%80%99s%20Desperation%20in%20Bengal%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04115522%2FGAG5kTgagAA1aoM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%20one%20can%20stop%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20told%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20November%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMamata%20Banerjee%20is%20opposing%20the%20CAA%2C%20but%20let%20me%20say%20it%20clearly%20that%20CAA%20will%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said%2C%20three%20days%20after%20junior%20home%20minister%20Ajay%20Mishra%20assured%20a%20gathering%20of%20the%20Matua-Namasudra%20population%20in%20West%20Bengal%20that%20the%20rules%20under%20the%20Act%20would%20be%20framed%20before%20March%2030%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarch%2030%20is%20likely%20to%20coincide%20with%20the%20peaking%20of%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revival%20of%20the%20CAA%20issue%2C%20which%20had%20taken%20a%20backseat%20since%20its%20passage%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20has%20intrigued%20political%20observers%20as%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20trigger%20protests%20in%20the%20northeastern%20states%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98sensitive%E2%80%99%20region%20already%20tense%20because%20of%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2Fnewsite%2FPrintRelease.aspx%3Frelid%3D195783%5C%22%3Epassed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20parliament%20on%20December%2011%2C%202019%2C%20allows%20citizenship%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%2C%20Parsis%20or%20Christians%20from%20the%20Muslim-majority%20countries%20of%20Afghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20or%20Pakistan%20who%20came%20to%20India%20before%202015.%20However%2C%20the%20rules%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20framed.%20Without%20the%20rules%2C%20the%20implementation%20cannot%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20framing%20the%20rules%2C%20the%20deadline%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20January%209%2C%202024%2C%20and%20for%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20it%20is%20March%2030.%20We%20will%20get%20it%20done%20by%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mishra%20said%20at%20an%20event%20in%20the%20Bangladesh-bordering%20Thakurnagar%20area%20of%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20North%2024-Parganas%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThakurnagar%20is%20the%20place%20where%20the%20main%20socio-religious%20organisation%20of%20the%20community%2C%20the%20Matua%20Mahasangha%2C%20is%20headquartered.%20The%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.peepultree.world%2Flivehistoryindia%2Fstory%2Feras%2Fbengals-namasudras%5C%22%3EMatua-Namasudras%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0are%20Hindu%20migrants%20from%20Bangladesh%20and%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fwebsite%2Fstory%2Findia-news-bjp-wins-pro-caa-matua-votes-but-caa-to-hit-mamata-hurdle%2F381943%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20voteries%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20CAA%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20CAA%20is%20never%20seen%20in%20isolation%20but%20as%20a%20precursor%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%20citizenship%20screening%20exercise%20at%20the%20national%20level%20in%20the%20style%20of%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20in%20Assam%2C%20as%20Shah%20had%20earlier%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F947436%2Fwho-is-linking-citizenship-act-to-nrc-here-are-five-times-amit-shah-did-so%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHe%2520even%252C%2520usefully%252C%2520includes%2520the%2Cthe%2520link%2520between%2520the%2520two.%5C%22%3Eclarified%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20NRC%20would%20be%20implemented%20only%20after%20ensuring%20the%20citizenship%20rights%20of%20the%20migrants%20belonging%20to%20the%20aforementioned%20six%20religions%20through%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohan%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20Comments%20on%20Manipur%20Violence%20Show%20Northeast%20Remains%20a%20Puzzle%20That%20RSS%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Solve%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmohan-bhagwat-comments-manipur-violence-northeast-puzzle%5C%22%3EMohan%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20Comments%20on%20Manipur%20Violence%20Show%20Northeast%20Remains%20a%20Puzzle%20That%20RSS%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Solve%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20had%20triggered%20different%20reactions%20in%20different%20regions.%20In%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Matua-Namasudra%20community%20%E2%80%93%20which%20made%20up%20about%204%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Census%20of%202001%20%E2%80%93%20welcomed%20the%20legislation%20but%20mostly%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20partial%20fulfilment%20of%20their%20demand%20for%20flawless%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20northeastern%20states%2C%20political%20parties%20and%20student%20organisations%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcaa-protest-northeast-indigenous%5C%22%3Eopposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20legalise%20illegal%20immigration.%20Various%20opposition%20parties%20opposed%20it%20for%20what%20they%20called%20the%20anti-Muslim%20discrimination%20inherent%20in%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20Matua-Namasudras%20have%20identity%20documents%20like%20voter%20ID%2C%20PAN%20and%20Aadhaar%20but%20face%20difficulties%20in%20getting%20police%20verification%20reports%20for%20passports%2C%20jobs%20and%20caste%20certificates%20when%20they%20are%20asked%20to%20produce%20records%20of%20their%20or%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20name%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20pre-1971%20voter%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Shah%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcaa-implemented-after-covid-19-vaccination-ends-amit-shah%5C%22%3Eblamed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20delay%20in%20framing%20rules%20on%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20However%2C%20the%20continued%20delay%20had%20left%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Matua%20populations%20upset%2C%20with%20many%20feeling%20betrayed%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20comments%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20West%20Bengal%20industries%20minister%20and%20senior%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20spokesperson%20Shashi%20Panja%20reiterated%20chief%20minister%20and%20party%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20promise%20that%20the%20CAA%20would%20not%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20has%20remembered%20the%20CAA%20because%20the%20elections%20are%20nearing.%20Over%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20they%20kept%20seeking%20extension%20after%20extension%2C%20nine%20extensions%20altogether%2C%20for%20framing%20the%20rules.%20The%20issue%20will%20again%20die%20when%20the%20elections%20are%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20at%20a%20press%20meet.%C2%A0The%20TMC%20has%20always%20maintained%20that%20the%20Matua-Manasudras%20are%20already%20citizens%20and%20do%20not%20need%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20who%20is%20involved%20in%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20Matua%20outreach%20programme%2C%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20delay%20is%20that%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Matua-Namasudra%20community%20members%20wanted%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcrg.ac.in%2FPP109.pdf%5C%22%3Eunconditional%20citizenship%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20They%20are%20opposed%20to%20any%20provision%20requiring%20them%20to%20file%20an%20application%20declaring%20themselves%20as%20a%20refugee%20and%20any%20provision%20related%20to%20providing%20proof%20of%20religious%20persecution%20in%20Bangladesh%20or%20any%20self-declaration%20attesting%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20such%20unconditionality%20could%20trigger%20unrest%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20it%20was%20feared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20comment%2C%20the%20All%20Assam%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%20(AASU)%E2%80%99s%20chief%20advisor%2C%20Samujjal%20Bhattacharjya%2C%20said%20that%20they%20would%20oppose%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20has%20exempted%20the%20inner-line%20cover%20areas%20and%20Sixth%20Schedule%20areas%20from%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20CAA.%20If%20CAA%20is%20bad%20for%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20areas%20and%20inner-line%20cover%20areas%2C%20how%20can%20it%20be%20good%20for%20Assam%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Northeast%3F%E2%80%9D%20Bhattacharjya%20reportedly%20asked%20during%20a%20local%20TV%20channel%20debate%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fpolitics%2F281123%2Fassam-oppn-parties-against-caa-implementation-union-minister-remark.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Chronicle%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Can%20Congress%20Victory%20in%20Bengal%20Assembly%20Bypoll%20Have%20Any%20Larger%20Implications%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-victory-west-bengal-bypoll-implications%5C%22%3ECan%20Congress%20Victory%20in%20Bengal%20Assembly%20Bypoll%20Have%20Any%20Larger%20Implications%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirmal%20Payeng%2C%20a%20youth%20leader%20of%20independent%20Assam%20MLA%20Akhil%20Gogoi%E2%80%99s%20Raijor%20Dal%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0they%20would%20oppose%20the%20CAA.%20A%20leader%20of%20the%20North%20East%20Students%E2%80%99%20Organisation%20(NESO)%2C%20which%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fnortheast-observes-black-day-observed-on-third-caa-anniversary%2Farticle66251402.ece%5C%22%3Eobserves%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0every%20December%2011%20as%20%E2%80%98black%20day%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98anti-CAA%20day%E2%80%99%2C%20said%20they%20would%20issue%20a%20statement%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Assam%2C%20protests%20are%20expected%20in%20the%20states%20of%20Meghalaya%20and%20the%20tribal-dominated%20areas%20of%20Tripura%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolarisation%20and%20the%20numbers%20game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ayan%20Guha%2C%20author%20of%20the%202022%20book%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Curious%20Trajectory%20of%20Caste%20in%20West%20Bengal%20Politics%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20pitch%20for%20the%20CAA%20seems%20to%20be%20directed%20towards%20the%20Namasudra-Matua%20refugees%2C%20as%20the%20community%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20restless%20due%20to%20the%20inordinate%20delay%20in%20finalising%20the%20rules%20for%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20large%20section%20of%20the%20community%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%202021%20assembly%20elections%20because%20of%20this%20promise.%20It%20is%20important%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20the%20Namasudra%20support%20base%20to%20repeat%20its%202019%20electoral%20success%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%E2%80%9D%20Guha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20will%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20party%20to%20navigate%20contradictory%20pulls%20and%20pressures%20emanating%20from%20different%20regions%20of%20the%20country%20on%20this%20issue.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20appears%20that%2C%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%20the%20party%20is%20prioritising%20its%20Namasudra%20support%20base%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Matua-Namasudra%20support%20is%20essential%20for%20winning%20the%20Bongaon%20and%20Ranaghat%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20of%20southern%20West%20Bengal%20and%20can%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20Barasat%20and%20Dum%20Dum%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20won%20Bongaon%20and%20Ranaghat%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%20revealed%20the%20Matua-Namasudra%20community%20in%20North%2024-Parganas%20and%20Nadia%20districts%20were%20an%20exception%20among%20which%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20support%20did%20not%20erode%20in%20the%20previous%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaidul%20Islam%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Studies%20in%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20Calcutta%20(CSSSC)%2C%20feels%20that%20the%20revival%20of%20the%20CAA%20issue%20shows%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20prioritised%20the%20numbers%20game.%20An%20issue%20like%20CAA%20is%20not%20only%20important%20in%20the%20Matua-Namasudra-dominated%20constituencies%20but%20also%20for%20larger%20polarisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20have%20to%20retain%20their%202019%20tally%20of%2018%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20from%20the%20state%2C%20or%20to%20increase%20it%2C%20they%20have%20no%20other%20option%20but%20creating%20polarisation%20on%20issues%20like%20the%20CAA%20and%20Ram%20Temple.%20They%20must%20have%20calculated%20that%20they%20have%20more%20seats%20in%20Bengal%20where%20they%20can%20gain%20by%20such%20polarisation%20than%20what%20they%20may%20have%20to%20lose%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%E2%80%9D%20Islam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETripura%20and%20Meghalaya%20have%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20each%20and%20Assam%20has%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Full%20Text%20%7C%20BJP's%20Exclusion%20of%20Muslims%20Is%20'Unacceptably%20Barbaric'%2C%20Says%20Amartya%20Sen%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ffull-text-bjps-exclusion-of-muslims-is-unacceptably-barbaric-says-amartya-sen%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Exclusion%20of%20Muslims%20Is%20%E2%80%98Unacceptably%20Barbaric%E2%80%99%2C%20Says%20Amartya%20Sen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20TMC%2C%20by%20unnecessarily%20targeting%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20during%20the%20ongoing%20session%2C%20was%20actually%20helping%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20polarisation%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Zaad%20Mahmood%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20Presidency%20University%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20said%20that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20the%20BJP%20finally%20backed%20out%20of%20its%20promise%20using%20some%20pretext.%20The%20BJP%20is%20used%20to%20speaking%20in%20different%20languages%20while%20addressing%20different%20crowds%20and%20mixes%20the%20promises%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20with%20some%20bluffs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20can%20speak%20the%20language%20of%20cow-vigilante%20lynching%20gangs%20of%20central%2C%20northern%20and%20western%20India%20who%20target%20Muslims%20for%20their%20food%20habits.%20They%20can%20also%20address%20the%20beef-consuming%20Hindus%20and%20tribals%20of%20Goa%20and%20northeast%20India.%20Their%20success%20lies%20in%20their%20ability%20to%20keep%20people%20in%20confusion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahmood%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20thinks%20that%20in%20case%20the%20BJP%20finally%20goes%20ahead%20with%20publishing%20the%20rules%2C%20fully%20knowing%20its%20implications%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20it%20would%20mean%20they%20are%20so%20desperate%20about%20getting%20the%20required%20numbers%20that%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20sacrifice%20the%20issue%20of%20national%20security%20by%20allowing%20more%20protests%20to%20break%20out%20in%20the%20already-volatile%20northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPublishing%20the%20draft%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%20would%20mean%20that%20they%20feel%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20from%20Bengal%20by%20creating%20a%20sharp%20polarisation%20is%20absolutely%20essential%20for%20them.%20In%20the%20numbers%20game%2C%20the%20northeast%20matters%20little%20when%20compared%20to%20West%20Bengal%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahmood%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701673227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04115522%2FGAG5kTgagAA1aoM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdoes-bjps-revival-of-the-caa-issue-reflect-the-partys-desperation-in-bengal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20revival%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20despite%20possible%20protests%20in%20the%20northeast%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Manipur%20has%20seen%20severe%20ethnic%20conflict%2C%20has%20triggered%20curiosities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdoes-bjps-revival-of-the-caa-issue-reflect-the-partys-desperation-in-bengal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranveer%20poses%20with%20SLB%2C%20Sara%20at%20Sharmin's%20wedding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701673055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105720344%2Cimgsize-145140.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-singhs-selfie-with-sanjay-leela-bhansali-sara-ali-khan-poses-with-the-new-bride-inside-pics-from-sharmin-segals-reception%2Farticleshow%2F105720344.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105720344.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESharmin%20Segal%20