pproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fj-kumar-infraprojects-bags-construction-order-worth-rs-379-crore-in-mumbai-123120400287_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fj-kumar-infraprojects-bags-construction-order-worth-rs-379-crore-in-mumbai-123120400287_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ASTRO's%20agency%20shuts%20Moonbin's%20memorial%20space%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701672383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105719906%2Cimgsize-13482.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fastros-agency-abruptly-shuts-moonbins-memorial-space-firmly-denies-allegations-of-financial-interest-and-threatens-legal-action%2Farticleshow%2F105719975.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105719975.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFantagio%20has%20announced%20immediate%20closure%20of%20Moonbin's%20memorial%20space%2C%20Seonunsa%20Temple%20Moon%20Space%2C%20due%20to%20suspicions%20of%20a%20business%20agreement%20between%20Fantagio%20and%20Seonunsa%20Temple.%20Fantagio%20has%20denied%20any%20financial%20interest%20and%20clarified%20that%20the%20relocation%20was%20for%20safety%20concerns%20and%20to%20enshrine%20a%20permanent%20memorial%20tablet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fastros-agency-abruptly-shuts-moonbins-memorial-space-firmly-denies-allegations-of-financial-interest-and-threatens-legal-action%2Farticleshow%2F105719975.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Why%20Congress'%20Telangana%20Win%20Complicates%20INDIA%20Strategy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP%203-0%20in%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20with%20a%20consolation%20win%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20party%20failed%20to%20save%20its%20governments%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20or%20exploit%20the%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20almost%2020-year-old%20BJP%20government%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20its%20win%20against%20the%20BRS%20in%20Telangana%20does%20bode%20well%20for%20its%20revival%20in%20southern%20India%2C%20the%20state%20sends%20only%2017%20MPs%20to%20parliament.%20The%20three%20states%20that%20the%20Congress%20lost%20send%20a%20combined%2065%20MPs%20to%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20losses%20have%20seriously%20weakened%20the%20Congress's%20position%20in%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc.%20The%20party%20hoped%20that%20a%20good%20performance%20in%20these%20state%20elections%20would%20establish%20its%20dominance%20over%20the%20grouping.%20Instead%2C%20it%20has%20lost%20the%20moral%20authority%20to%20even%20lead%20such%20an%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegional%20parties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20and%20even%20DMK%20-%20a%20Congress%20ally%20-%20will%20now%20demand%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20seats%20in%20their%20states%20and%20will%20strongly%20resist%20a%20Congress%20leader%20being%20projected%20as%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20face%20of%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20an%20important%20constituent%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20have%20soured%20over%20seat%20adjustments%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Both%20parties%20have%20hinted%20they%20could%20go%20it%20alone%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20country's%20most%20populous%20and%20politically%20crucial%20state.%20The%20Congress%20has%20lost%20its%20bargaining%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegional%20parties%20like%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU)%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20have%20expressed%20their%20displeasure%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20seat%20sharing%20talks%2C%20the%20common%20minimum%20program%2C%20and%20the%202024%20campaign%20because%20of%20the%20Congress's%20preoccupation%20with%20the%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20is%20celebrating%20its%20victory%20in%20Telangana%20and%20its%20spokespersons%20are%20highlighting%20how%20they%20have%20trounced%20a%20regional%20party.%20Yet%2C%20the%20party%20is%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20dependent%20on%20regional%20parties%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20didn't%20have%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20beat%20the%20BJP%20on%20its%20own%20as%20its%20presence%20was%20limited%20to%20261%20seats%20(less%20than%2050%25%20of%20house%20strength)%20in%202019.%20Here%20is%20where%20the%20issue%20gets%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20won%20Karnataka%20earlier%20this%20year%20gaining%20largely%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20regional%20party%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20(JDS).%20It%20squeezed%20out%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda's%20party%2C%20making%20the%20contest%20bipolar%20as%20the%20BJP%20maintained%20its%20vote%20share.%20The%20Congress%20ate%20into%20the%20minority%20and%20Scheduled%20Caste%2FScheduled%20Tribes%20vote%20bank%20of%20the%20JDS%2C%20which%20suffered%20its%20second%20worst%20performance%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20similar%20story%20in%20Telangana%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20gained%208%25%20ST%2C%2013%25%20SC%20and%205%25%20Muslim%20support%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20BRS%2C%20denting%20almost%2010%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20KCR-led%20party.%20The%20BJP%20too%20gained%207%25%20vote%20share%20in%20the%20state.%20Again%2C%20the%20Congress%20gained%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20a%20regional%20party%20without%20touching%20the%20support%20base%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20lost%20significant%20support%20of%20OBCs%2C%20SC-ST%2C%20and%20Muslims%20to%20regional%20parties%20in%20the%20north%20and%20south%2C%20like%20SP%2C%20RJD%2C%20TMC%2C%20AAP%2C%20BRS%2C%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%2C%20BJD%2C%20and%20NCP.%20The%20core%20voters%20of%20many%20regional%20parties%20are%20complementary%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDS%20formed%20an%20alliance%20for%20the%20first%20time%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%2C%20and%20transferred%20its%20vote%20base%20to%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20in%20seats%20it%20did%20not%20contest%2C%20including%20its%20key%20Vokkaliga%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20voters%2C%20including%20members%20of%20the%20minority%20community%2C%20did%20not%20return%20to%20the%20JDS%20in%20the%202023%20Karnataka%20election%2C%20leaving%20it%20with%20half%20its%20previous%20tally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20regional%20parties%20are%20apprehensive%20of%2C%20and%20this%20fear%20could%20grow%20stronger%20after%20the%20Congress's%20Telangana%20victory.%20Any%20regional%20party%20collaborating%20with%20the%20Congress%20could%20permanently%20lose%20its%20Muslim%20and%20SC-ST%20vote%20base%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Congress%20too%2C%20it%20is%20far%20easier%20to%20make%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20vote%20share%20of%20regional%20parties%20than%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20enjoys%20the%20support%20of%20the%20upper%20castes%20and%20OBCs%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%2C%20two%20sections%20that%20have%20proved%20difficult%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20crack%20for%20years.%20The%20caste%20census%20dice%20it%20has%20thrown%20is%20not%20working%2C%20as%20the%20state%20election%20results%20reveal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20called%20for%20the%20next%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20partners%20on%20December%206%20in%20Delhi.%20That%20meeting%20promises%20to%20be%20turbulent%2C%20with%20some%20parties%20already%20taking%20aim%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20what%20some%20of%20them%20describe%20as%20its%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ezamindari%3C%2Fem%3E%20mindset%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJDU%20leader%20Nikhil%20Mandal%2C%20slamming%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20over%20the%20party's%20triple%20defeat%2C%20suggested%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20should%20be%20led%20by%20his%20boss%2C%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20He%20said%20the%20Congress%20ignored%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20because%20of%20its%20fixation%20with%20the%20state%20elections%20and%20still%20did%20not%20perform.%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20he%20added%2C%20was%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20alliance%20and%20is%20capable%20of%20navigating%20the%20ship%20through%20choppy%20waters.%20Trinamool%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20said%20on%20social%20media%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20three%20states%2C%20it%20is%20more%20of%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20Congress%20than%20the%20success%20of%20the%20BJP%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20confident%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20predicting%20a%20hat-trick%20in%202024%2C%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%20is%20back%20to%20square%20one%20after%20a%20successful%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20and%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%20victories%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Its%20poor%20performance%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20and%20victory%20in%20Telangana%20versus%20a%20regional%20party%20has%20complicated%20matters%20for%20a%20fragile%20opposition%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701672360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fu15rpqa8_telangana-congress_625x300_03_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-congress-telangana-win-complicates-india-strategy-4631404%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Its%20poor%20performance%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20and%20victory%20in%20Telangana%20versus%20a%20regional%20party%20has%20complicated%20matters%20for%20a%20fragile%20opposition%20alliance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-congress-telangana-win-complicates-india-strategy-4631404%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-congress-telangana-win-complicates-india-strategy-4631404%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-congress-telangana-win-complicates-india-strategy-4631404%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mitchell%20Johnson%20Slams%20David%20Warner's%20%26quot%3BHero's%20Sendoff%26quot%3B%2C%20Selector%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralia's%20squad%20selection%20for%20the%20Test%20series%20against%20Pakistan%20hasn't%20been%20without%20controversy.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22David%20Warner%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1285-david-warner-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDavid%20Warner%3C%2Fa%3E's%20inclusion%20in%20the%20series%20hasn't%20gone%20down%20well%20with%20former%20Australia%20star%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Johnson%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F749-mitchell-johnson-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Johnson%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Aussie%20opener%2C%20while%20also%20reigniting%20the%20ball-tampering%20controversy.%20Johnson%2C%20in%20his%20criticism%20for%20Warner%2C%20said%20that%20the%20southpaw%20doesn't%20deserve%20a%20%26quot%3Bhero's%20sendoff%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20series%20being%20his%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20that%2C%20Johnson%20also%20targeted%20Australia's%20chief%20selector%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22George%20Bailey%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1222-george-bailey-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGeorge%20Bailey%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20selectoring%20Warner%20despite%20his%20poor%20Test%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20then-captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Tim%20Paine%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1343-tim-paine-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETim%20Paine%3C%2Fa%3E's%20career%20was%20ending%20over%20the%20sexting%20controversy%2C%20chairman%20of%20selectors%20George%20Bailey%20said%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20deciding%20Paine's%20fate%20because%20the%20pair%20were%20close%20friends.%20The%20handling%20of%20Warner%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20who%20played%20with%20Bailey%20in%20all%20three%20forms%2C%20raises%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20Bailey%20was%20simply%20too%20quickly%20out%20of%20playing%20and%20into%20the%20job%20and%20too%20close%20to%20some%20of%20the%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Johnson%20in%20his%20column%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewest.com.au%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Fmitchell-johnson-david-warner-does-not-deserve-a-farewell-test-series-after-ball-tampering-disgrace-c-12763238%5C%22%3EThe%20West%20Australian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Bailey%20was%20asked%20about%20Johnson's%20comments%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20hopes%20the%20latter%20is%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20sent%20little%20snippets%20of%20it.%20I%20hope%20he's%20OK.%20I've%20got%20no%20idea%20%5Bif%20he%20is%5D.%20My%20only%20observation%20would%20be%20if%20someone%20can%20show%20me%20how%20being%20distant%20and%20unaware%20of%20what%20players%20are%20going%20through%20and%20what%20the%20plans%20are%20with%20the%20team%20and%20with%20the%20coaching%20staff%2C%20how%20that's%20more%20beneficial%2C%20I'd%20be%20all%20ears%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bailey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20Of%20Pakistan%20Tests%2C%20Australia%20Chief%20Selector%20Responds%20To%20Mitchell%20Johnson's%20Criticism%20Of%20David%20Warner%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20Warner's%20record%20in%20Tests%20is%20concerned%2C%20he%20has%20featured%20in%20109%20Test%20matches%20for%20Australia%2C%20scoring%208487%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2044.33.%20In%20tota%2C%20he%20has%20scored%2025%20hundreds%20and%2036%20half-centuries%20in%20his%20red-ball%20career%20for%20the%20Aussies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202020%2C%20however%2C%20Warner's%20Test%20average%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20just%2031.79.%20Yet%2C%20Bailey%20feels%20he%20is%20one%20of%20Australia's%20finest%20players%20in%20the%20longest%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20we%20still%20think%20he's%20in%20our%20best%2011%20players%20to%20win%20the%20first%20Test.%20I%20think%20Test%20cricket%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20way%20that%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20points%20are%20set%20up%2C%20each%20Test%20is%20critical.%20There're%20points%20on%20the%20line%20for%20each%20and%20every%20game.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BSo%20our%20focus%20is%20very%20much%20on%20picking%20the%2011%20that%20we%20think%20can%20do%20the%20job%20and%20obviously%20there're%20roles%20within%20that%20for%20each%20individual%20and%20how%20that%20actually%20structures%20up%20the%20team%20as%20a%20whole%3B%20and%20we%20think%20David%20is%20the%20right%20person%20for%20that%20for%20this%20Test%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bailey%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBailey%20admitted%20that%20Australia%20are%20in%20the%20hunt%20to%20find%20Warner's%20successor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20ability%20to%20put%20the%20opposition%20under%20pressure%20is%20pretty%20special%2C%20and%20not%20to%20be%20taken%20lightly.%20Whenever%20you've%20had%20someone%20who's%20had%20that%20longevity%20and%20been%20so%20dominating%20in%20a%20role%2C%20(it's%20important)%20just%20to%20temper%20the%20expectations%20of%20whoever%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20replacement%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20back%20to%20Warnie%20finishing%20up%20as%20a%20spinner%20and%20how%20many%20spinners%20got%20brought%20in%20and%20shuffled%20out%20in%20the%20quest%20to%20almost%20try%20and%20replicate%20Warnie.%20I%20don't%20think%20you%20ever%20try%20and%20replicate%20someone%20who's%20played%20a%20role%20for%20as%20long%20as%20someone%20has%20done%20it%20as%20well%20as%20they%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20put%20David%20in%20that%20category%2C%20the%20way%20he's%20opened%20the%20batting%20for%20Australia%20for%20such%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time.%20So%20that's%20something%20that%20we're%20certainly%20conscious%20of%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20fit%20post-David%20is%20the%20right%20one.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701671940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Fjsg3i7n_david-warner-test-afp_625x300_31_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fahead-of-pakistan-tests-australia-chief-selector-responds-to-mitchell-johnsons-criticism-of-david-warner-4629157%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Australia's%20chief%20selector%20has%20responded%20to%20Mitchell%20Johnson's%20criticism%20of%20David%20Warner%20ahead%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Test%20series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fahead-of-pakistan-tests-australia-chief-selector-responds-to-mitchell-johnsons-criticism-of-david-warner-4629157%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fahead-of-pakistan-tests-australia-chief-selector-responds-to-mitchell-johnsons-criticism-of-david-warner-4629157%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fahead-of-pakistan-tests-australia-chief-selector-responds-to-mitchell-johnsons-criticism-of-david-warner-4629157%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Drug%20That%20Causes%20%26quot%3BHoles%26quot%3B%20In%20Skin%20Spreading%20Across%20UK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20new%20breed%20of%20drugs%2050%20times%20more%20powerful%20than%20fentanyl%20is%20spreading%20fast%20across%20the%20UK%2C%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20said.%20The%20synthetic%20opioids%2C%20called%20nitazenes%2C%20are%20being%20cut%20into%20drugs%20like%20heroin.%20According%20to%20Alcohol%20and%20Drug%20Foundation%2C%20nitazenes%20were%20developed%20by%20researchers%20around%2060%20years%20ago%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20morphine%2C%20but%20because%20of%20their%20high%20potential%20for%20overdose%20were%20never%20released.%20These%20drugs%2C%20often%20mixed%20with%20fentanyl%20or%20other%20drugs%2C%20have%20been%20connected%20to%20a%20number%20of%20overdose%20deaths%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20seeing%20people%20coughing%20up%20blood.%20I'm%20seeing%20people%20dying.%20Any%20drug%20you%20are%20buying%20off%20the%20street%20you're%20taking%20a%20risk.%20These%20people%20are%20in%20it%20for%20the%20money%20and%20the%20purer%20it%20is%2C%20the%20less%20they%20make%20-%20so%20they%20are%20putting%20other%20stuff%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Rory%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20East%20London%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnitazenes-the-new-synthetic-opioids-stronger-than-heroin-that-are-being-cut-into-drugs-13020356%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFentanyl%20is%2050%20times%20stronger%20than%20heroin%20and%20is%20the%20primary%20drug%20in%20North%20America%2C%20where%20synthetic%20opioids%20are%20estimated%20to%20have%20caused%2075%2C000%20deaths%20in%20the%20US%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitazenes%20have%20similar%20properties%20to%20fentanyl%2C%20but%20can%20be%20up%20to%20300%20times%20stronger%20than%20heroin%2C%20Sky%20News%20said%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20who%20suffered%20the%20dangerous%20consequences%20of%20nitazene%20use%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%20what%20she%20had%20to%20go%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20got%20holes%20in%20my%20legs.%20There's%20no%20skin%2C%20just%20holes.%20It's%20painful%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20said%20pointing%20towards%20her%20bandaged%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20strange%20bores%20in%20her%20flesh%20have%20only%20appeared%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%20The%20woman's%20name%20has%20not%20been%20released%20by%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitazenes%20were%20first%20discovered%20in%20the%20UK%20in%202021%2C%20from%20a%20sample%20of%20white%20powder%20found%20in%20the%20back%20of%20a%20taxi%20in%20Wakefield.%20They%20have%20since%20been%20found%20in%20heroin%2C%20cannabis%2C%20cocaine%2C%20in%20a%20vape%20and%20most%20prevalently%20in%20black%20market%20pills%20sold%20as%20the%20anti-anxiety%20drug%20diazepam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInflow%20of%20synthetic%20drugs%20increased%20due%20to%20Taliban%20crackdown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdirahim%20Hassan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20campaigning%20against%20the%20drug%2C%20said%20the%20Taliban%20conducted%20a%20crackdown%20on%20heroin%20production%20in%20Afghanistan%20that%20successfully%20stemmed%20the%20flow%20of%20heroin%20from%20the%20country.%20Afghanistan%20had%20previously%20provided%2095%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20UK%20heroin%20market%2C%20but%20the%20move%20led%20to%20a%20boom%20in%20the%20easier%20to%20produce%2C%20more%20deadly%20synthetics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20it%20means%20is%20there's%20a%20much%20higher%20risk%20of%20overdose%20and%20death.%20But%20it's%20a%20cheaper%20product%20and%20more%20potent%20so%20people%20are%20in%20greater%20crisis%20and%20there%20is%20not%20enough%20testing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Sky%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20nitazenes%20look%20like%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20drugs%20are%20sold%20as%20a%20white%20powder%2C%20crystalline%20solid%2C%20or%20brown%2Fyellow%20powder%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadf.org.au%2Fdrug-facts%2Fnitazenes%2F%5C%22%3EAlcohol%20and%20Drug%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20have%20also%20been%20found%20in%20tablets%20(fake%20oxycodone)%2C%20heroin%2C%20ketamine%20and%20synthetic%20cannabinoids.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701671760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F7du48uk_drugs-generic-unsplash_625x300_04_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnitazenes-drug-50-times-powerful-than-fentanyl-spreading-across-uk-causes-holes-in-skin-4631721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nitazenes%20were%20first%20discovered%20in%20the%20UK%20in%202021%2C%20from%20a%20sample%20of%20white%20powder%20found%20in%20the%20back%20of%20a%20taxi%20in%20Wakefield.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnitazenes-drug-50-times-powerful-than-fentanyl-spreading-across-uk-causes-holes-in-skin-4631721%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnitazenes-drug-50-times-powerful-than-fentanyl-spreading-across-uk-causes-holes-in-skin-4631721%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnitazenes-drug-50-times-powerful-than-fentanyl-spreading-across-uk-causes-holes-in-skin-4631721%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Better%20than%20ETCS%3F%20Railways%20wants%20to%20export%20Kavach%20tech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701671510000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105719405%2Cimgsize-75558.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fbetter-than-european-train-control-system-indian-railways-can-export-kavach-tech-in-5-years-says-ashwini-vaishnaw%2Farticleshow%2F105718941.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20Railways%20plans%20to%20implement%20Kavach%20technology%20across%20its%20entire%20network%20to%20eliminate%20train%20collisions%20caused%20by%20human%20error.%20The%20installation%20will%20increase%20to%205%2C000%20km