E%20Days%20after%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20directed%20colleges%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fugc-urges-universities-to-set-up-narendra-modi-selfie-points-on-campuses-to-foster-pride%5C%22%3Eto%20create%20selfie%20points%20featuring%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20background%2C%20the%20regulatory%20body%20has%20withdrawn%20the%20suggested%20designs%20linked%20to%20the%20directive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20directive%20received%20significant%20backlash%2C%20with%20many%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20equivalent%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccult-building%E2%80%9D%20exercise%20while%20others%20called%20it%20a%20campaign%20for%20Modi%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulatory%20body%20did%20not%20specify%20why%20the%20designs%20were%20being%20withdrawn%20while%20the%20directive%20to%20set%20up%20the%20selfie%20points%20remains%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20UGC%20official%20on%20Saturday%20said%20modified%20designs%20might%20be%20issued%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fugc-takes-a-step-back-on-selfies-withdraws-designs-with-pm-photos-after-criticism%2Fcid%2F1984342%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fugc-urges-universities-to-set-up-narendra-modi-selfie-points-on-campuses-to-foster-pride%5C%22%3EUGC%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20directive%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20each%20selfie%20point%20should%20be%20established%20at%20a%20strategic%20place%20on%20the%20campus%20and%20have%20a%203D%20layout.%20It%20also%20recommended%20various%20themes%20like%20internationalisation%20of%20education%2C%20unity%20in%20diversity%2C%20Smart%20India%20Hackathon%2C%20Indian%20knowledge%20system%2C%20multilingualism%2C%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20rise%20in%20higher%20education%2C%20research%20and%20innovation%20for%20the%20photo-ops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproved%20designs%20related%20to%20each%20theme%20were%20available%20on%20a%20Google%20Drive%20link%20attached%20to%20the%20UGC%E2%80%99s%20letter.%20Each%20design%20carried%20a%20large%20image%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20with%20certain%20representative%20pictures%20on%20the%20theme%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fugc-takes-a-step-back-on-selfies-withdraws-designs-with-pm-photos-after-criticism%2Fcid%2F1984342%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20folder%20has%20been%20empty%20since%20Saturday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20UGC%20secretary%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20neither%20the%20regulator%20nor%20any%20educational%20institution%20had%20ever%20before%20been%20involved%20in%20promoting%20government%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fugc-directs-maharashtra-universities-to-celebrate-rss-abvp-leaders-birth-centenary%5C%22%3EUGC%20Directs%20Maharashtra%20Universities%20to%20Celebrate%20RSS-ABVP%20Leader%E2%80%99s%20Birth%20Centenary%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20the%20present%20UGC%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20Jagadesh%20Kumar%20is%20openly%20doing%20publicity%20for%20the%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20former%20UGC%20secretary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fugc-takes-a-step-back-on-selfies-withdraws-designs-with-pm-photos-after-criticism%2Fcid%2F1984342%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20the%20job%20of%20the%20UGC.%20All%20government%20institutions%20and%20autonomous%20bodies%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20impartial.%20(But%20the)%20UGC%20is%20gradually%20becoming%20a%20wing%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20Telegraph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20bureaucrat%20said%20that%20decision-making%20in%20the%20UGC%20used%20to%20be%20participative%20but%20%E2%80%9Cnow%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20one-way%20communication%2C%20and%20nobody%20else%20is%20allowed%20to%20speak.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20many%20circulars%20are%20being%20sent%20to%20universities%2C%20with%20directives%20on%20almost%20every%20subject%2C%20that%20there%20is%20no%20space%20for%20creativity%20by%20any%20institution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaya%20John%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20academic%20council%20of%20Delhi%20University%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20UGC%E2%80%99s%20letter%20on%20selfie%20points%20represented%20an%20overreach.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20as%20a%20university%20community%20are%20supposed%20to%20critically%20engage%20with%2C%20not%20valorise%2C%20the%20regime.%20We%20see%20the%20UGC%E2%80%99s%20letter%20as%20a%20breach%20in%20terms%20of%20its%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fugc-takes-a-step-back-on-selfies-withdraws-designs-with-pm-photos-after-criticism%2Fcid%2F1984342%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20unnecessary%20political%20interference.%20Universities%20are%20an%20autonomous%20open%20space%3B%20they%20are%20required%20to%20be%20kept%20autonomous.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20on%20selfie%20points%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20another%20such%20directive%20where%20the%20UGC%20had%20urged%20institutes%20of%20higher%20education%20in%20Maharashtra%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fugc-directs-maharashtra-universities-to-celebrate-rss-abvp-leaders-birth-centenary%5C%22%3Ecelebrate%20the%20birth%20centenary%20year%20of%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20leader%20Dattaji%20Didolkar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701671372000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29095001%2FScreenshot-2023-11-29-at-9.49.41-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ft