%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Franbir-kapoor-animal-napoleon-hunger-games-box-office-1235820070%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Franbir-kapoor-animal-napoleon-hunger-games-box-office-1235820070%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Morning%20After%3A%2015%20Takeaways%20From%20the%20Four%20State%20Election%20Results%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03225531%2FGAb8Es9bAAAeQQI.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E1.%20In%20the%20three%20north%20Indian%20states%20where%20assembly%20elections%20were%20held%2C%20Rajasthan%20elects%2025%20MPs%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2011%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2029.%20Of%20the%20total%20of%2065%20MPs%20these%20add%20up%20to%2C%20all%20except%20one%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20three%20from%20Chhattisgarh%20%E2%80%93%20i.e.%2C%2061%20MP%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20are%20held%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20since%202019.%20Any%20shock%20here%20in%20the%20just-concluded%20elections%20would%20have%20spelt%20trouble%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20The%20party%20may%20not%20have%20expanded%20its%20influence%20with%20governments%20beyond%20safe%20quarters%20since%202019%20as%20it%20might%20have%20hoped%20to%2C%20having%20lost%20in%20Karnataka%20earlier%20this%20year%20and%20then%20in%20Telangana%2C%20but%20winning%20state%20elections%20here%20means%20its%20core%20is%20secure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Of%20the%20four%20states%20for%20which%20we%20saw%20results%20on%20Sunday%2C%20three%20states%20threw%20out%20their%20governments.%20Two%20Congress%20chief%20ministers%20were%20unseated%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS).%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%2C%20KCR%2C%20lost%20in%20Kamareddy%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20seats%20he%20contested.%20Anti-incumbency%20is%20a%20theme.%20BJP%20should%20celebrate%20that%20it%20came%20out%20on%20top.%20But%20should%20it%20also%20worry%2C%20as%20it%20shifts%20gears%20into%202024%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20a%20ten-year%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20that%20anti-incumbency%20is%20a%20thing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20With%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-shivraj-singh-chouhan%5C%22%3Eemerging%20as%20an%20impossible%20opponent%20to%20dislodge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20the%20new%20Gujarat%3F%20The%20BJP%20has%20always%20won%20a%20higher%20vote%20share%20than%20the%20Congress%20this%20millennium%20(including%202018%20when%20the%20Congress%20had%20more%20seats).%20This%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20first%20states%20to%20be%20ruled%20by%20the%20forebearers%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20since%201977.%20So%2C%20what%20exactly%20makes%20them%20tick%20here%20needs%20introspection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22To%20Defeat%20BJP%20in%20an%20Increasingly%20Bipolar%20India%2C%20the%20Congress%20Would%20Need%20Much%20More%20Passion%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-madhya-pradesh-rajasthan-chhattisgarh-bjp-congress-election%5C%22%3ETo%20Defeat%20BJP%20in%20an%20Increasingly%20Bipolar%20India%2C%20the%20Congress%20Would%20Need%20Much%20More%20Passion%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20The%20BJP%2C%20till%20as%20recently%20as%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiUgCoW_0g44%5C%22%3E%20Karnataka%20in%20May%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20used%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Cdouble%20engine%E2%80%9D%20to%20ask%20voters%20in%20assembly%20elections%20to%20vote%20for%20it%2C%20as%20it%20would%20make%20everything%20smoother%20%E2%80%93%20like%20hitching%20your%20wagon%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdouble%20engine%E2%80%9D.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20there%20was%20no%20talk%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdouble%20engine%E2%80%9D.%20Three%20Union%20ministers%20were%20asked%20to%20contest%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20several%20MPs%20too%20were%20pushed%20into%20the%20fray%20in%20both%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20a%20direct%20line%20was%20drawn%20to%20Delhi.%20The%20Modi-centric%20campaign%20effectively%20sidelined%20three%20once-powerful%20BJP%20chief%20ministers%2C%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20Raman%20Singh%20and%20Shivraj%20Chouhan.%20%3Cem%3EKaun%20Bangea%20Mukhya%20Mantri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Who%20will%20be%20chief%20minister)%20now%2C%20may%20offer%20clues%20about%20the%20next-gen%20BJP%20that%20is%20being%20envisaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20play%20inside%20the%20BJP%20paradigm%3F%20%E2%80%98North%20India%20has%20gone%20Hindutva%2C%E2%80%99%20so%20%E2%80%98let%20us%20go%20Hindutva%20too%2C%E2%80%99%20seemed%20to%20be%20Kamal%20Nath%20and%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20plan.%20But%20stealing%20playbooks%20has%20limited%20political%20appeal%20when%20such%20a%20dominant%20player%20is%20in%20your%20face%2C%20and%20established%20as%20the%20real%20thing.%20Hindutva-lite%20may%20actually%20serve%20to%20enhance%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20appeal%2C%20as%20it%20works%20on%20accepting%20the%20rules%20set%20by%20the%20real%20thing.%20The%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20thinking%20on%20this%20may%20need%20a%20reboot.%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20politics%20may%20not%20be%20the%20answer%20to%20%3Cem%3Ekamal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(lotus).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Modi%20has%20ditched%20the%20double-engine%20sway%20he%20offered%20voters%20till%20the%20UP%20elections%20last%20year.%20Now%2C%20with%20the%20government%20putting%20out%20official%20ads%20terming%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98Modi%20government%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Modi%20guarantee%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20organisational%20structure%20may%20look%20spanking%20but%20it%20is%20under%20strain.%20Watch%20out%20for%20whether%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%2C%20also%20OBC%20and%20with%20a%20longer%20stay%20at%20the%20crease%20than%20Modi%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20or%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20the%20sidelined%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20will%20accept%20being%20pushed%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Three%20Things%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Definitive%20Victory%20in%20the%20Assembly%20Elections%20Tells%20Us%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthree-things-bjps-definitive-victory-in-the-assembly-elections-tells-us%5C%22%3EThree%20Things%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Definitive%20Victory%20in%20the%20Assembly%20Elections%20Tells%20Us%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bharat-rashtra-samithi-congress-kcr%5C%22%3ETelangana%20win%20for%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20decisive%20up%20from%20the%2028.43%25%20it%20had%2C%20though%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20TDP%20in%202018%2C%20to%2039.5%25%20this%20time%2C%20must%20be%20savoured%20as%20it%20signals%20a%20return%20in%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20Telugu%20states%20for%20the%20Congress.%20A%20rare%20thing%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20trump%20a%20powerful%20regional%20party%20and%20to%20recover%20in%20a%20state%20where%20its%20machinery%20had%20been%20rusting%20and%20defunct%20for%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20Telangana%20also%20signals%20that%20regional%20parties%20in%20the%20vicinity%20%E2%80%93%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(TDP%20and%20YSRCP)%2C%20Odisha%20(BJD)%20and%20West%20Bengal%20(TMC)%20%E2%80%93%20may%20be%20more%20wary%20of%20the%20Congress%20now.%20Could%20this%20make%20getting%20INDIA%20together%20trickier%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20In%20Telangana%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20%E2%80%93%20Hyderabad%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%E2%80%99s%20party%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20Congress%20exchanged%20sharp%20words%20throughout%20the%20campaign%20and%20the%20Congress%20won%20the%20state%20in%20firm%20opposition%20to%20the%20party.%20Could%20this%20give%20pause%20to%20Owaisi%E2%80%99s%20plans%20to%20expand%20on%20to%20Congress%20or%20INDIA%20areas%3F%20Owaisi%E2%80%99s%20party%20has%20held%20its%20own%20in%20seven%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Why%20Congress%20Lost%20in%20Three%20States%20and%20Won%20in%20One%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congress-lost-in-three-states-and-won-in-one%5C%22%3EWhy%20Congress%20Lost%20in%20Three%20States%20and%20Won%20in%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10.%20Would%20it%20have%20helped%20if%20the%20Congress%20had%20continued%20to%20march%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20INDIA%20tune%20in%20these%20elections%2C%20to%20just%20help%20create%20a%20different%20political%20mood%20and%20prevent%20erosion%20of%20votes%20in%20these%20tough%20fights%3F%20Should%20it%20have%20stitched%20up%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Left%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Adivasi%20Party%20in%20Rajasthan%3F%20The%20Congress%20maintained%20its%20vote-share%2C%20but%20that%20is%20cold%20comfort%20as%20the%20BJP%20added%20many%20more%2C%20like%20the%20Jogi%20Congress%20voters%2C%20in%20its%20fold%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20ran%20away%20with%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E11.%20Would%20a%20%E2%80%98humbled%E2%80%99%20Congress%20be%20a%20better%20team%20leader%20for%20INDIA%3F%20Or%20have%20ties%20with%20allies%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20many%20others%20frayed%20irretrievably%3F%20Life%20is%20bound%20to%20get%20more%20interesting%2C%20not%20easier%2C%20for%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E12.%20What%20is%20with%20welfare%3F%20The%20campaign%20has%20as%20much%20to%20offer%20as%20the%20results.%20%E2%80%98Competitive%20welfarism%E2%80%99%20was%20in%20full%20swing.%20But%20so%20was%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekind%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20welfare.%20Rajasthan%20offered%20a%20unique%20model%20of%20not%20just%20hand-outs%20but%20healthcare%2C%20social%20security%2C%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%20and%20a%20model%20more%20close%20to%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%2C%20than%20other%20states%20in%20north%20India.%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Eladli%20behna%3C%2Fem%3E%20school%20of%20welfare%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20may%20suggest%20that%20governments%20conclude%20it%20is%20okay%20to%20privatise%20healthcare%20and%20education%2C%20as%20long%20as%20direct%20cash%20or%20hand-outs%20can%20be%20given.%20The%20ruling%20BJP%20may%20be%20encouraged%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22For%20BJP%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20Leap%20in%20Seats%2C%20a%20Jump%20in%20Vote%20Share%20and%20a%20Reversal%20of%202018%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-shivraj-singh-chouhan%5C%22%3EFor%20BJP%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20Leap%20in%20Seats%2C%20a%20Jump%20in%20Vote%20Share%20and%20a%20Reversal%20of%202018%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E13.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20always%20work%20well%20to%20jump%20parties.%20Several%20marquee%20candidates%20who%20defected%2C%20lost.%20Jyoti%20Mirdha%2C%20ex-Congress%20MP%2C%20lost%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Incidentally%2C%20her%20grandfather%2C%20Congressman%20Ram%20Niwas%20Mirdha%20was%20amongst%20the%20two%20only%20winners%20in%20north%20India%20for%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20in%201977.%20Another%20ex-Congress%20Union%20minister%2C%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20now%20a%20Union%20minister%20in%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20government%2C%20found%2010%20of%20his%2016%20supporters%20trailing.%20Five%20of%20these%20were%20ministers%20in%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E14.%20The%20caste%20census%20is%20coming%20under%20fire.%20Is%20it%20a%20political%20dud%3F%20Those%20opposing%20it%20or%20even%20those%20proposing%20it%20would%20do%20well%20to%20remember%20that%20it%20is%20no%20instant%20political%20fix.%20If%20indeed%20it%20is%20to%20be%20deployed%20politically%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20powered%20by%20an%20expansive%20campaign%2C%20especially%20in%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20which%20are%20feudal%20plus%20lacking%20a%20dominant%20OBC%20group%20which%20could%20take%20the%20issue%20and%20run%20with%20it%2C%20like%20in%20neighbouring%20UP%20or%20Bihar.%20After%20all%2C%20in%20Telangana%2C%20the%20BJP%20promised%20it%20would%20make%20a%20%E2%80%9CBC%20chief%20minister%E2%80%9D%2C%20something%20it%20might%20not%20have%20said%20if%20the%20caste%20census%20would%20not%20have%20been%20made%20a%20talking%20point%20by%20the%20opposition.%20It%20is%20more%20social%20project%20than%20political%20slogan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E15.%20That%20a%20%E2%80%98Modi%20guarantee%E2%80%99%20campaign%20came%20through%20would%20mean%20the%20Centre%20would%20feel%20super-charged%20the%20morning%20after.%20What%20might%20that%20mean%20for%20impunity%2C%20which%20we%20have%20already%20seen%20rise%20in%20ample%20measure%3F%20This%20year%20saw%20dismal%20shows%20in%20the%20V-Dem%20score%2C%20Freedom%20House%20report%20and%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20Index.%20Will%20the%20popular%20mandate%20in%20crucial%20states%20fuel%20more%20of%20the%20same%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701653440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03225531%2FGAb8Es9bAAAeQQI.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-morning-after-15-takeaways-from-the-four-state-election-results%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Of%20the%20four%20states%20for%20which%20we%20saw%20results%20on%20Sunday%2C%20three%20states%20threw%20out%20their%20governments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-morning-after-15-takeaways-from-the-four-state-election-results%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20Mizoram's%20Voters%20Consider%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20a%20Poll%20Issue%3F%20Today's%20Results%20Will%20Tell.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13225738%2FThe-Wire-40.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20With%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20deferring%20the%20date%20for%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20polled%20in%20the%20November%207%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Mizoram%20by%20a%20day%2C%20the%20process%20is%20unrolling%20at%208%20am%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20unprecedented%20step%20to%20revise%20the%20counting%20date%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20ECI%20in%20response%20to%20a%20massive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fmizoram-churches-pray-change-counting-date-assembly-polls%5C%22%3Euproar%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%2C%20since%20the%20previous%20date%20of%20December%203%20fell%20on%20a%20Sunday%2C%20an%20auspicious%20day%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Christian-majority%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20state%20election%20commission%2C%204%2C000%20officials%20would%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20counting%20exercise%20for%20the%2040%20assembly%20constituencies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EState%20chief%20electoral%20officer%20Madhup%20Vyas%20had%20told%20reporters%20that%20a%20full%20dress%20rehearsal%20for%20counting%20was%20held%20though%20the%20ENCORE%20portal%20on%20November%2030.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22248%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%2C%2013%20counting%20centres%20across%20the%20state%20have%20been%20readied.%20As%20many%20as%2040%20counting%20halls%20in%20the%20centres%20would%20count%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commission%20said%20the%20officials%20would%20work%20on%20399%20electronic%20voting%20machine%20(EVM)%20tables%20and%2056%20postal%20ballot%20tables%20to%20complete%20the%20exercise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ruling%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20is%20seeking%20a%20second%20consecutive%20term%20in%20these%20elections%20while%20facing%20unprecented%20anti-incumbency%20mounted%20by%20another%20regional%20entity%2C%20the%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20(ZPM).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20ZPM%20contested%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20pocketed%20eight%20of%20the%2025%20seats%20it%20had%20contested%2C%20while%20the%20MNF%20wrested%20power%20from%20the%20Congress%20with%20wins%20in%2026%20seats.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MNF%20could%20restrict%20the%20Congress%20in%20five%20seats%20after%20two%20terms%20in%20power.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20pocketed%20only%20one%20seat%20in%20the%20Chakma%20belt%20and%20failed%20to%20convince%20the%20MNF%2C%20its%20NDA%20ally%2C%20to%20accommodate%20party%E2%80%99s%20sole%20MLA%20within%20its%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMizoram%20has%2C%20therefore%2C%20remained%20the%20only%20state%20in%20the%20northeast%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20in%20the%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20though%2C%20the%20ZPM%20has%20emerged%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20MNF.%20Several%20exit%20polls%20have%20predicted%20a%20clean%20sweep%20for%20the%20ZPM%2C%20placing%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%20third%20and%20fourth%20positions%20respectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20buzz%20in%20the%20state%20is%20that%20the%20ZPM%20is%20close%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20is%20to%20be%20seen%20after%20today%20if%20the%20national%20party%20could%20enter%20the%20next%20Mizoram%20government.%20The%20election%20results%20will%20also%20show%20if%20the%20BJP%20could%20have%20an%20MLA%20from%20the%20majority%20Mizo%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Mizos%20were%20upset%20with%20the%20ruling%20party%20for%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20Kukis%20of%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20with%20whom%20they%20share%20fraternal%20relations%20%E2%80%93%20during%20the%20recent%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20that%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMizoram%20chief%20minister%20and%20MNF%20supremo%20Zoramthanga%20not%20only%20became%20a%20voice%20of%20the%20Kuki-Mizo%20communities%20with%20New%20Delhi%20during%20the%20violence%2C%20but%20also%20raised%20it%20as%20an%20election%20issue%20during%20his%20campaign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29143618%2FZoramthanga-at-solidarity-march-1024x768.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29143618%2FZoramthanga-at-solidarity-march-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29143618%2FZoramthanga-at-solidarity-march-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F29143618%2FZoramthanga-at-solidarity-march.jpeg%201152w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665774%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EZoramthanga%20at%20a%20solidarity%20march%20for%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20in%20Aizawl%20on%20July%2026.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40ITFLMedia_Cell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20publicly%20said%20he%20would%20not%20share%20a%20platform%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20if%20the%20latter%20campaigned%20in%20the%20state%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20Modi%20did%20not%20visit%20the%20Kuki%20community%20in%20Manipur%20during%20the%20violence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUltimately%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-gives-mizoram-election-rally-a-miss-is-manipur-mayhem-the-reason%5C%22%3EModi%20cancelled%20his%20campaigning%20trip%20to%20Mizoram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20it%20the%20only%20poll-bound%20state%20that%20he%20skipped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20their%20respective%20campaigns%2C%20the%20ZPM%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20played%20down%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20violence%20and%20instead%20accused%20the%20MNF%20government%20of%20financial%20mismanagement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDecember%204%20will%20decide%20whether%20Mizos%20regarded%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20state%20as%20a%20poll%20issue.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20ZPM%20trips%20the%20MNF%20after%20the%20counting%20of%20the%20votes%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20second%20regional%20party%20to%20have%20grabbed%20power%20in%20Mizoram.%20The%20state%20would%20also%20break%20out%20of%20an%20over-three-decade-long%20cycle%20of%20the%20exchange%20of%20power%20between%20the%20MNF%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701653402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2