%20cooperation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20his%20return%20to%20Mal%C3%A9%2C%20President%20Muizzu%20told%20reporters%20that%20%E2%80%9Can%20agreement%20had%20been%20reached%20to%20withdraw%20Indian%20military%20personnel%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20in%20progress%20at%20a%20technical%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresidency.gov.mv%2FPress%2FArticle%2F29265%5C%22%3Epress%20release%20issued%20by%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20recalled%20that%20he%20had%20held%20a%20series%20of%20constructive%20meetings%20and%20dialogues%20with%20the%20Indian%20government.%20Since%20winning%20the%20election%20on%20September%2030%2C%20he%20engaged%20in%20two%20discussions%20with%20the%20Indian%20high%20commissioner%20to%20Mal%C3%A9%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Indian%20delegation%20during%20his%20inaugural%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20he%20had%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20discussions%20we%20had%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20agreed%20to%20remove%20Indian%20soldiers%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Findia-agrees-withdraw-soldiers-maldives-president-muizzu-2023-12-03%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20said%20on%20Sunday%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20level%20committee%E2%80%9D%20had%20been%20set%20up%20%E2%80%9Cto%20solve%20issues%20related%20to%20development%20projects%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20no%20official%20comment%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20but%20a%20few%20hours%20later%2C%20Indian%20official%20sources%20said%20that%20the%20issue%20was%20%E2%80%9Cbriefly%20discussed%E2%80%9D%20in%20Dubai%20at%20the%20discussions%20between%20the%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20sources%20described%20the%20issue%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstatus%20of%20Indian%20platforms%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20Maldives%20engaged%20in%20HADR%20%5Bhumanitarian%20assistance%20and%20disaster%20relief%5D%20activities%E2%80%9D%2C%20since%20the%20Indian%20defence%20personnel%20had%20been%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives%20to%20operate%20two%20helicopters%20and%20a%20Dornier%20aircraft%20for%20medical%20evacuation%20purposes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDiscussions%20on%20how%20to%20keep%20them%20operational%20are%20ongoing.%20The%20core%20group%20that%20both%20sides%20have%20agreed%20to%20set%20up%20will%20look%20at%20details%20of%20how%20to%20take%20this%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20side%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccontinued%20usefulness%20of%20the%20Indian%20platforms%E2%80%9D%20had%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Clooked%20at%20in%20a%20proper%20perspective%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20Maldivian%20government%20%E2%80%9Chas%20acknowledged%20the%20utility%20of%20these%20platforms%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20an%20important%20segment%20of%20our%20bilateral%20development%20partnership%20is%20recognised%20by%20both%20sides%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20official%20sources%20contested%20the%20Maldivian%20president%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20the%20bilateral%20panel%E2%80%99s%20focus%20was%20solely%20on%20expediting%20Indian%20development%20projects.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20they%20clarified%20that%20the%20agreed-upon%20objective%20was%20to%20explore%20solutions%20on%20keeping%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20helicopters%20and%20Dornier%20aircraft%20operational%2C%20which%20was%20obviously%20linked%20with%20the%20stationing%20of%20Indian%20personnel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20major%20promise%20of%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20election%20campaign%20had%20been%20to%20remove%20Indian%20troops%20from%20the%20Maldives.%20He%20claimed%20the%20troops%20hindered%20the%20island%20nation%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20after%20he%20was%20sworn%20in%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmaldives-president-asks-india-to-withdraw-its-troops%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20formally%20requested%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20withdraw%20the%20Indian%20troops%20from%20Maldivian%20soil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20senior%20official%20at%20the%20new%20Maldivian%20president%E2%80%99s%20office%20had%20also%20publicly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.presidencymaldives.gov.mv%2FPress%2FArticle%2F29102%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edisclosed%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20there%20were%2077%20Indian%20troops%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%2050%20personnel%20were%20engaged%20in%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20two%20choppers%2C%20while%20the%20Dornier%20aircraft%20required%2025%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701626818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03232814%2FMuizzu-and-Modi.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmaldives-claims-agreement-troop-withdrawal-but-india-says-discussions-ongoing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20major%20promise%20of%20Maldives%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20election%20campaign%20had%20been%20to%20remove%20Indian%20troops%20from%20the%20Maldives.%20He%20claimed%20the%20troops%20hindered%20the%20island%20nation%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F