calUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Fassembly-election%2Fhat-trick-in-states-guarantee-of-hat-trick-in-2024-says-pm-narendra-modi-123120301104_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Fassembly-election%2Fhat-trick-in-states-guarantee-of-hat-trick-in-2024-says-pm-narendra-modi-123120301104_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Fassembly-election%2Fhat-trick-in-states-guarantee-of-hat-trick-in-2024-says-pm-narendra-modi-123120301104_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Congress's%20Cautious%20Pessimism%20Proves%20to%20Be%20Too%20Little%2C%20Too%20Late%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03221624%2FGAbGmIJXgAAqeBc.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaipur%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20stunning%20move%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20won%2054%20seats%2C%20going%20beyond%20every%20expectation%20and%20even%20the%20exit%20polls%2C%20released%20a%20day%20prior%2C%20to%20sweep%20the%20state%20in%20the%20assembly%20election.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20faced%20a%20massive%20loss%2C%20with%20only%20a%20few%20ministers%20apart%20from%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20managing%20to%20save%20their%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20established%20an%20early%20lead%2C%20winning%20all%2014%20seats%20in%20the%20Sarguja%20region%20and%20eight%20out%20of%2012%20in%20the%20Bastar%20region.%20The%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20senior%20leader%20T.S.%20Singh%20Deo%20lost%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rajesh%20Agarwal%20by%2094%20votes%20in%20the%20Ambikapur%20seat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20seats%20the%20Congress%20managed%20to%20win%2C%20Sukma%E2%80%99s%20Konta%20constituency%20was%20hotly%20contested.%20Minister%20Kawasi%20Lakhma%20managed%20to%20save%20his%20seat%20by%201%2C930%20votes%20against%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20leader%20Manish%20Kunjam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20home%20minister%20Tamradhwaj%20Sahu%20and%20agriculture%20minister%20Ravindra%20Chaubey%20also%20lost%2C%20with%20Chaubey%20losing%20it%20to%20a%20political%20newbie%2C%20Ishwar%20Sahu.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESahu%2C%20who%20had%20lost%20his%20son%20in%20the%20religious%20violence%20in%20Kawardha%2C%20fought%20his%20campaign%20on%20religious%20lines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20vote%20share%20stayed%20stagnant%20at%2042%25%2C%20the%20BJP%20increased%20its%20vote%20share%20to%20slightly%20above%2046%25%2C%20showing%20a%20significant%20rise%20in%20pro-BJP%20sentiments%20among%20the%20voters.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20state%20capital%20Raipur%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20all%20seven%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20fought%20the%20election%20with%20no%20CM%20face%2C%20and%20after%20the%20win%2C%20the%20party%20is%20now%20in%20a%20mad%20rush%20to%20finalise%20a%20name.%20Former%20chief%20minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Raman%20Singh%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20party%20had%20not%20expected%20this%20majority.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20now%20clear%20that%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20residents%20were%20done%20with%20the%20corruption%20of%20the%20Congress%20government.%20We%20managed%20to%20show%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20mismanagement%20that%20they%20were%20involved%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Baghel%2C%20who%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20win%20more%20than%2075%20seats%20this%20time%2C%20managed%20to%20win%20his%20constituency%2C%20Patan%2C%20with%20a%20margin%20of%20over%2010%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20political%20experts%2C%20the%20party%20lost%20out%20majorly%20on%20urban%20voters.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20political%20analyst%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CUrban%20voters%20also%20help%20building%20the%20image%20which%20the%20Congress%20failed%20to%20capture.%20They%20also%20seem%20to%20have%20lost%20out%20to%20the%20Mahtari%20Vandan%20Yojana%2C%20despite%20making%20a%20bigger%20promise%2C%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fulfil%20all%20promises%20of%20direct%20debit%20transfer%20made%20last%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20did%20expect%20damage%20and%20was%20cautiously%20pessimistic%2C%20even%20though%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20deliver%20any%20strong%20message%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20experts%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20big%20shocks%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%20were%20from%20the%20Bastar%20and%20Sarguja%20regions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20star%20leader%20from%20Sarguja%20was%20promised%20a%20CM%20position%20and%20then%20denied%20it.%20Evidently%20the%20people%20of%20Sarguja%20are%20unhappy%20with%20this.%20The%20Congress%20dug%20its%20own%20grave%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20also%20faced%20significant%20dissatisfaction%20from%20tribal%20and%20minority%20communities%20for%20what%20they%20see%20is%20its%20%E2%80%9Csoft%20Hindutva%E2%80%9D%20ideology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701622060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03221624%2FGAbGmIJXgAAqeBc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-chhattisgarh-congresss-cautious-pessimism-proves-to-be-too-little-too-late%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20fought%20the%20election%20with%20no%20CM%20face%2C%20and%20after%20the%20win%2C%20the%20party%20is%20now%20in%20a%20mad%20rush%20to%20finalise%20a%20name.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-chhattisgarh-congresss-cautious-pessimism-proves-to-be-too-little-too-late%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22To%20Defeat%20BJP%20in%20an%20Increasingly%20Bipolar%20India%2C%20the%20Congress%20Would%20Need%20Much%20More%20Passion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03220137%2FGAb8HZ5aUAEE1HN.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%203-1%20outcome%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20belied%20most%20pre-poll%20predictions%20that%20showed%20the%20Congress%20to%20have%20an%20edge%20in%20at%20least%20three%20of%20the%20five%20poll-bound%20states.%20The%20results%20not%20only%20showcase%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20continuing%20dominance%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20but%20also%20reflects%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20challenge%20it%20effectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20can%20draw%20some%20succour%20from%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bharat-rashtra-samithi-congress-kcr%5C%22%3Espectacular%20revival%20in%20Telangana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20it%20was%20down%20and%20out%20until%20a%20year%20ago.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20its%20victory%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20appeared%20to%20be%20overshadowed%20by%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-shivraj-singh-chouhan%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%20The%20BJP%20returned%20to%20power%20for%20a%20fifth%20term%20by%20registering%20a%20thumping%20absolute%20majority%2C%20while%20ejecting%20the%20Congress%20governments%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20share%20of%20votes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chhattisgarh%20win%20will%20perhaps%20be%20the%20sweetest%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20dysfunctional%20leadership%20was%20believed%20by%20many%20as%20miles%20behind%20the%20Congress%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%20The%20BJP%20not%20only%20beat%20the%20odds%20in%20the%20central%20Indian%20state%20by%20leading%20a%20focused%20campaign%20against%20the%20alleged%20corruption%20during%20the%20Congress%20regime%20but%20also%20increased%20its%20vote%20share%20by%20a%20substantive%2013%20percentage%20points%20%E2%80%93%20from%2033%25%20to%2046%25.%20This%20accounts%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20win%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20largely%20retained%20its%20vote%20share.%20It%20had%20a%2043%25%20vote%20share%20in%202018%2C%20which%20came%20down%20marginally%20to%2042.19%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20veering%20close%20to%20getting%20almost%20165%20seats%20out%20of%20230%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20lags%20behind%20at%20a%20distant%2065.%20Here%20again%2C%20the%20Congress%20retained%20its%20vote%20share%20of%20a%20little%20over%2040%25%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20added%20a%20chunk%20to%20its%20votes%2C%20increasing%20its%20vote%20share%20from%20a%20little%20more%20than%2041%25%20to%20around%2049%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20BJP%20(41.69%25)%20edged%20past%20the%20Congress%20(39.53%25)%20by%20a%20thin%20margin%2C%20indicating%20what%20a%20close%20contest%20it%20was%2C%20although%20the%20final%20results%20do%20not%20reflect%20it%20well.%20The%20BJP%20won%20115%20seats%2C%20restricting%20the%20Congress%20to%2069.%20Yet%2C%20compared%20to%20its%20previous%20losses%2C%20the%20Congress%20performed%20respectably.%20Although%20the%20Congress%20largely%20retained%20its%202018%20vote%20share%20(39.3%25)%2C%20registering%20only%20a%20marginal%20gain%2C%20the%20BJP%20increased%20its%20vote%20share%20by%20over%20three%20percentage%20points.%20In%202018%2C%20it%20had%20slipped%20to%2038.08%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20results%2C%20once%20again%2C%20indicate%20that%20Indian%20elections%20are%20increasingly%20becoming%20bi-polar.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20brought%20its%20vote%20share%20close%20to%2050%25%20in%20most%20of%20the%20northern%20states.%20Any%20party%20that%20wants%20to%20upstage%20it%20will%20have%20to%20bear%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20and%20work%20accordingly.%20Gone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20in%20multi-cornered%20contests%2C%20parties%20used%20to%20form%20governments%20with%20around%2030%25%20votes.%20In%202012%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20won%20over%20200%20seats%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20assembly%20to%20form%20a%20government%20on%20its%20own%20with%20merely%2028%25%20votes.%20In%202007%2C%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20formed%20a%20government%20on%20its%20own%20in%20UP%20with%20a%20little%20over%2030%25.%20However%2C%20despite%20both%20these%20opposition%20parties%20coming%20together%20in%20an%20alliance%20to%20garner%20nearly%2040%25%20votes%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20it%20could%20not%20get%20past%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20alone%20received%20nearly%2050%25%20of%20the%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20has%20been%20a%20trend%20in%20almost%20all%20north%20Indian%20states%2C%20where%20BJP%20is%20establishing%20new%20benchmarks%20for%20Indian%20elections%20in%20successive%20rounds.%20This%20has%20helped%20the%20BJP%20oust%20incumbents%20from%20opposition%20and%20also%20retain%20its%20own%20governments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20Congress%20claims%20to%20have%20wiped%20out%20the%20BJP%20from%20the%20only%20southern%20state%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20southern%20states%20show%20a%20similar%20trend.%20If%2C%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%20or%20Kerala%2C%20the%20elections%20are%20fought%20between%20only%20two%20fronts%2C%20the%20winning%20party%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20registers%20over%2045%25%2C%20easily.%20In%20bi-polar%20fights%2C%20except%20in%20the%20recent%20case%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20shown%20its%20inability%20to%20dislodge%20incumbents.%20For%20instance%2C%20Kerala%2C%20too%2C%20beat%20the%20trend%20of%20overthrowing%20governments%20after%20every%20five%20year%20term%2C%20when%20the%20Congress-led%20alliance%20could%20not%20beat%20the%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20government%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congress-lost-in-three-states-and-won-in-one%5C%22%3EWhy%20Congress%20Lost%20in%20Three%20States%20and%20Won%20in%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Congress%20has%20had%20better%20chances%20at%20winning%20big%20if%20there%20are%20more%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20electoral%20fray.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Congress%20could%20form%20a%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20with%20around%2043%25%20against%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2038%25%2C%20as%20the%20third%20party%20in%20the%20fray%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%2C%20despite%20its%20worst-ever%20performance%2C%20could%20still%20register%20around%2013%25%20vote%20share.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20third%20party%2C%20although%20a%20smaller%20force%2C%20inadvertently%20ends%20up%20helping%20the%20Congress%20by%20amplifying%20the%20opposition%20narrative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20possibility%20which%20does%20not%20take%20away%20from%20the%20comprehensive%20nature%20of%20the%20grand%20old%20party%E2%80%99s%20win%20in%20Telangana%20is%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20doubling%20down%20its%20attack%20on%20the%20BRS%20government%20may%20have%20also%20helped%20the%20electorate%20sway%20towards%20the%20Congress%20wholeheartedly.%20It%20was%2C%20after%20all%2C%20the%20party%20best%20placed%20to%20replace%20the%20incumbent.%20This%20may%20be%20a%20minor%20observation%20in%20front%20of%20the%20spirited%2C%20focused%2C%20and%20aggressive%20campaign%20that%20the%20Congress%20led%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Telangana%2C%20especially%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20one%20it%20had%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20but%20it%20still%20holds%20ground.%20The%20BJP%20received%20around%2014%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%2C%20while%20the%20BRS%20with%2037.36%25%20and%20the%20Congress%20with%2039.39%25%20fought%20it%20out%20across%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20unlike%20Baghel%2C%20Gehlot%2C%20and%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20aggressively%20challenged%20the%20chief%20minister%20KCR.%20Reddy%20sent%20a%20simple%20message%20to%20the%20electorate%20that%20KCR%20regime%20symbolises%20a%20single%20family%E2%80%99s%20feudal%20rule%20that%20was%20responsible%20for%20widespread%20corruption%2C%20unemployment%2C%20and%20general%20economic%20stagnation.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20was%20aided%20by%20leaders%20like%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%20who%20led%20a%20state-wide%20foot%20rally.%20The%20Congress%20has%20much%20to%20learn%20from%20its%20victories%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%2C%20where%20its%20leadership%20was%20aggressive%20and%20creative%2C%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20constantly%20engaged%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMissing%20passion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilar%20hard%20work%20and%20spirit%20was%20missing%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%20The%20leaders%20remained%20either%20trapped%20in%20tackling%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20anti-Hindu%20perception%20in%20these%20states%20or%20could%20not%20articulate%20their%20achievements%20skilfully.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20Congress%20seems%20to%20suffer%20from%20a%20basic%20disconnect%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20as%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20the%20CM%20hopeful%2C%20did%20not%20come%20across%20as%20passionately%20articulating%20the%20resentment%20and%20anger%20found%20on%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%20The%20Congress%20alternative%20looked%20like%20a%20mirror%20image%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20nothing%20new%20to%20offer.%20The%20Chhattisgarh%20scenario%20also%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20same%20for%20Baghel%2C%20who%20tried%20his%20best%20to%20match%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20own%20game%2C%20while%20giving%20a%20free%20run%20to%20an%20allegedly%20corrupt%20administration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20assembly%20elections%20were%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20lose%2C%20as%20almost%20all%20post-poll%20surveys%20showed%20that%20the%20party%20had%20momentum%20on%20its%20side.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20superior%20election%20management%20skills%20and%20comparatively%20better%20organisational%20strength%20turned%20the%20tide%20in%20its%20favour.%20True%2C%20given%20a%20pliant%20media%20narrative%2C%20resource-rich%20BJP%2C%20and%20almost%20a%20blatant%20use%20of%20power%20against%20the%20opposition%20forces%2C%20the%20Congress%20does%20not%20have%20a%20level-playing%20field.%20Yet%2C%20any%20opposition%20force%20will%20have%20to%20beat%20all%20these%20odds%20if%20it%20participates%20in%20the%20elections%20and%20aspires%20to%20beat%20a%20dominant%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20nearly%2050%25%20vote%20share%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20a%20large%20number%20of%20states%20clearly%20implies%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20best%20positioned%20only%20if%20it%20receives%20the%20support%20of%20other%20political%20forces.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20it%20may%20have%20just%20squandered%20an%20opportunity%20to%20fight%20the%20elections%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA).%20These%20assembly%20polls%20could%20have%20been%20the%20first%20real%20experiment%20for%20the%20alliance%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20But%20it%20insisted%20on%20fighting%20alone%2C%20even%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20annoying%20its%20INDIA%20partners.%20The%20results%20are%20for%20everyone%20to%20see.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701621180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03220137%2FGAb8HZ5aUAEE1HN.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-madhya-pradesh-rajasthan-chhattisgarh-bjp-congress-election%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hard%20work%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20kind%20shown%20by%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%2C%20and%20earlier%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20was%20missing%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-madhya-pradesh-rajasthan-chhattisgarh-bjp-congress-election%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20war%3A%20Russia%20accused%20of%20killing%20unarmed%20Ukrainian%20prisoners%20of%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701619436000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F779D%2Fproduction%2F_131912603_29240d7c46191ada132a24cedd73e41c2a56ba38-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67607857%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kyiv%20investigates%20a%20video%20said%20to%20show%20two%20surrendering%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20being%20shot%20by%20Russians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A82%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67607857%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2