%22%3EThe%20group%20of%20farmers%20was%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20by%20selling%208%2C000%20pearls.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHarvesting%20pearls%20in%20water-scarce%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20pursuing%20a%20Diploma%20in%20Medical%20Laboratory%20Technology%20(DMLT)%2C%20Sanjay%20works%20part-time%20as%20a%20lab%20assistant.%20But%20farming%20comes%20naturally%20to%20him%20as%20for%20generations%2C%20his%20family%20has%20been%20cultivating%20traditional%20crops.%20However%2C%20agriculture%20hardly%20reaped%20the%20family%20any%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20year%2C%20we%20did%20not%20get%20rain%20at%20all.%20We%20did%20sow%20soybeans%20and%20other%20crops%2C%20but%20we%20did%20not%20get%20any%20output.%20It%20has%20become%20difficult%20to%20even%20earn%20back%20the%20input%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20back%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20even%20established%20a%20water%20bank%20in%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20for%20irrigation%20purposes.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20turned%20to%20fish%20farming%20to%20utilise%20the%20water%20bank%20but%20the%20initiative%20was%20dead%20in%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFish%20farming%20did%20not%20prove%20profitable%20for%20us%20as%20it%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20input%20costs.%20If%20we%20sold%20a%20fish%20for%20Rs%20100%2C%20we%20would%20incur%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2080.%20We%20were%20only%20left%20with%20Rs%2020%20profit.%20It%20was%20very%20little%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Sanjay%20came%20across%20a%20news%20report%20that%20mentioned%20the%20profitability%20of%20oyster%20pearl%20farming.%20Motivated%20to%20try%20his%20hands%20in%20cultivating%20oysters%2C%20he%20bought%2025%2C000%20oysters%20to%20cultivate%20in%20his%20water%20bank.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20also%20roped%20in%20other%20farmer%20friends